A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fus-cluster-munitions-delivered-to-ukraine%2Famp_articleshow%2F101745346.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Compelled%20Speech%2C%20Dissent%20and%20the%20National%20Anthem%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2F08214447%2Fnational-anthem-movie-halls-PTI.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20July%203%20in%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20(J%26amp%3BK)%2C%20there%20were%20conflicting%20reports%20of%2014%20policemen%2Fpersons%20having%20been%20arrested%2Fsuspended%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjk-11-men-sent-to-jail-for-a-week-for-not-standing-up-during-national-anthem%5C%22%3Eallegedly%20disrespecting%20the%20national%20anthem%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20the%20Srinagar%20police%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSrinagarPolice%2Fstatus%2F1676839438171750400%5C%22%3Etweet%3C%2Fa%3E%20clarified%20that%2012%20persons%20had%20been%20generally%20bound%20down%20for%20good%20behaviour%20under%20sections%20107%20and%20151%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20(CrPC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%20107%20of%20the%20CrPC%20empowers%20the%20executive%20magistrate%20to%20order%20a%20person%20to%20execute%20a%20bond%20for%20keeping%20peace%20and%20public%20tranquillity%20for%20a%20specified%20duration%20not%20exceeding%20one%20year%2C%20while%20Section%20151%20of%20the%20CrPC%20gives%20preventive%20detention%20powers%20to%20the%20police%20without%20a%20warrant%20from%20a%20magistrate%2C%20in%20case%20they%20have%20knowledge%20of%20any%20design%20to%20commit%20a%20cognisable%20offence%20by%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alleged%20crime%20committed%20by%20these%2012%20people%3A%20not%20rising%20for%20the%20national%20anthem%20at%20an%20event%20called%20%E2%80%98Pedal%20for%20Peace%E2%80%99%20organised%20by%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20on%20May%2025.%20J%26amp%3BK%20lieutenant%20governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20was%20in%20attendance%2C%20and%20it%20is%20reported%20that%20after%20he%20took%20serious%20note%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20proceedings%20were%20initiated%20against%20these%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPursuant%20to%20an%20order%20by%20the%20Srinagar%20executive%20magistrate%2C%20on%20July%203%2C%20the%20accused%20were%20sent%20to%20the%20Srinagar%20central%20jail%20under%20preventive%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOffence%20of%20disrespecting%20the%20national%20anthem%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%203%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiacode.nic.in%2Fbitstream%2F123456789%2F15401%2F1%2Finsults_to_national_honour_act%252C_1971.pdf%5C%22%3EPrevention%20of%20Insult%20to%20National%20Honour%20Act%2C%201971%3C%2Fa%3E%20provides%20for%20the%20punishment%20of%20imprisonment%20of%20up%20to%20three%20years%20and%2For%20a%20fine%20for%20anyone%20preventing%20the%20singing%20of%20the%20national%20anthem%20or%20causing%20disturbance%20to%20any%20assembly%20engaged%20in%20singing%20the%20national%20anthem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20neither%20does%20the%20said%20statute%20provide%20any%20provision%20for%20an%20offence%20regarding%20%E2%80%98disrespect%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20national%20anthem%2C%20nor%20does%20it%20define%20what%20entails%20disrespect%20to%20the%20national%20anthem.%20What%20the%20Act%20criminalises%20is%20the%20prevention%20of%20the%20singing%20of%20the%20national%20anthem%20or%20causing%20disturbance%20to%20an%20assembly%20engaged%20in%20the%20singing%20of%20the%20national%20anthem%20%E2%80%93%20plain%20and%20simple!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fkashmir-respect-national-symbols-fear%5C%22%3EIn%20Kashmir%2C%20Respect%20for%20National%20Symbols%20Cannot%20Be%20Commanded%20By%20Fear%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20fundamental%20tenet%20of%20criminal%20jurisprudence%20that%20penal%20statutes%20are%20to%20be%20strictly%20construed.%20Thus%2C%20a%20law%20that%20defines%20any%20offence%20and%20provides%20for%20any%20punishment%20cannot%20be%20given%20a%20broad%20interpretation%2C%20and%20in%20case%20of%20any%20ambiguity%2C%20the%20accused%20under%20such%20a%20provision%20is%20to%20be%20acquitted%20rather%20than%20being%20held%20guilty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20whether%20refusing%20to%20sing%20or%20stand%20for%20the%20national%20anthem%20amounts%20to%20an%20offence%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Insult%20to%20National%20Honour%20Act%20or%20not%2C%20I%20would%20argue%20for%20the%20latter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20%3Cem%3EBijoe%20Emmanuel%20%26amp%3B%20Ors.%20%3C%2Fem%3E(1986)%20had%20come%20to%20the%20rescue%20of%20three%20children%20belonging%20to%20the%20Jehovah%E2%80%99s%20Witnesses%20sect%20who%20were%20suspended%20from%20their%20school%20for%20not%20singing%20the%20national%20anthem%2C%20holding%20that%20forcing%20the%20children%20to%20sing%20the%20national%20anthem%20violated%20their%20right%20to%20religion%20under%20Article%2025%20of%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20%3Cem%3EBijoe%20Emmanuel%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecategorically%20held%20that%20there%20is%20no%20provision%20of%20law%20which%20obliges%20anyone%20to%20%E2%80%98sing%E2%80%99%20the%20national%20anthem%2C%20it%20did%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F1508089%2F%5C%22%3Eemphasise%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20fundamental%20duty%20of%20citizens%20under%20Article%2051-A%20(a)%20of%20the%20constitution%20%E2%80%9Cto%20abide%20by%20the%20constitution%20and%20respect%20the%20national%20flag%20and%20national%20anthem%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20essence%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20held%20that%20it%20would%20not%20be%20disrespectful%20to%20the%20national%20anthem%20if%20a%20person%20stood%20respectfully%20when%20it%20was%20sung%20but%20did%20not%20join%20the%20singing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20times%2C%20the%20controversy%20regarding%20standing%20for%20the%20national%20anthem%20resurfaced%20when%20in%202016%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20%3Cem%3EShyam%20Narayan%20Chouksey%20%3C%2Fem%3E(2018)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fnational-anthem-films-supreme-court%5C%22%3Epassed%20an%20interim%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20directing%20all%20movie%20theatres%20to%20mandatorily%20play%20the%20national%20anthem%20before%20the%20start%20of%20a%20film%20and%20further%20directed%20that%20everyone%20present%20in%20the%20theatre%20must%20stand%20to%20show%20respect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20purported%20reason%20behind%20the%20direction%20was%20to%20%E2%80%9Cinstil%20committed%20patriotism%20and%20nationalism%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Creflect%20love%20and%20respect%20for%20the%20motherland%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fpatriotism-cinema-national-anthem%5C%22%3EPatriotism%2C%20Coming%20Soon%20to%20a%20Cinema%20Near%20You%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20it%20was%20felt%20mandatory%20for%20the%20audience%20to%20project%20patriotism%20and%20nationalism%20before%20watching%20a%20steamy%20Emraan%20Hashmi%20romance%20or%20a%20gritty%20Tom%20Cruise%20thriller%20is%20beyond%20my%20understanding.%20To%20the%20contrary%2C%20I%20would%20argue%20that%20such%20an%20imposition%20trivialises%20the%20value%20and%20dignity%20of%20the%20act%20of%20showing%20respect%20to%20the%20national%20anthem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20good%20sense%20prevailed%20and%20the%20bizarre%20interim%20order%20in%20%3Cem%3EShyam%20Narayan%20Chouksey%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcinema-owners-can-decide-whether-to-play-national-anthem-but-mandatory-to-stand-if-played-sc%5C%22%3Emodified%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202018%2C%20and%20the%20playing%20of%20the%20national%20anthem%20in%20theatres%20was%20made%20optional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20interim%20(and%20sometimes%20even%20after%20the%20order%20was%20made%20optional)%2C%20there%20were%20several%20untoward%20incidents%20reported%20in%20theatres%2C%20where%20overzealous%20patriots%20and%20self-proclaimed%20nationalists%20heckled%20and%20physically%20and%20verbally%20abused%20their%20fellow%20citizens%20for%20not%20sharing%20their%20own%20enthusiasm%20when%20the%20national%20anthem%20was%20played%2C%20to%20the%20point%20where%20even%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fyou-know-that-the-enforcing-patriotism-has-gone-out-of-control-when-a-wheelchair-bound-man-is-beaten-up-in-a-movie-hall-for-not-standing-up-during-the-national-anthem-263843.html%5C%22%3Ewheelchair-bound%20moviegoer%20was%20not%20spared%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20not%20standing%20up%20during%20the%20playing%20of%20the%20national%20anthem!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F97902638%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDr.%20Tawseef%20Ahmed%20Bhatt%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2021)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20high%20court%20held%20that%20not%20standing%20up%20while%20the%20national%20anthem%20is%20being%20sung%2C%20or%20standing%20up%20but%20not%20singing%20the%20national%20anthem%20along%20with%20members%20of%20an%20assembly%20engaged%20in%20such%20singing%2C%20may%20amount%20to%20disrespect%20to%20the%20national%20anthem%20and%20a%20failure%20to%20adhere%20to%20fundamental%20duties%20enumerated%20in%20Part%20IVA%20of%20the%20constitution%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20same%20is%20not%20an%20offence%20as%20defined%20under%20section%203%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Insult%20to%20National%20Honour%20Act.%20It%20was%20further%20held%20by%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20high%20court%20that%20the%20fundamental%20duties%20enumerated%20in%20Part%20IVA%20of%20the%20constitution%20are%20also%20not%20enforceable%20in%20law%20and%20the%20breach%20of%20such%20duties%20is%20not%20an%20offence%20under%20any%20penal%20law%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECompelled%20speech%20in%20a%20democracy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%2019%20(1)%20(a)%20of%20the%20constitution%20guarantees%20to%20the%20citizens%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression.%20The%20state%20can%20curtail%20this%20right%20by%20imposing%20reasonable%20restrictions%20on%20multiple%20grounds%2C%20like%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20sovereignty%20and%20integrity%20of%20India%2C%20the%20security%20of%20the%20state%2C%20public%20order%2C%20decency%20or%20morality%2C%20etc.%20as%20provided%20under%20Article%2019%20(2).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20existence%20of%20these%20restrictions%20are%20certainly%20essential%20in%20a%20democracy%2C%20especially%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20day%20and%20age%2C%20when%20one%20gets%20to%20hear%20instances%20of%20hate%20speech%20targeted%20against%20minorities%20everyday%20by%20no%20less%20than%20sitting%20parliamentarians%20and%20lawmakers%20shouting%20slogans%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fanurag-thakur-delhi-chants%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Edesh%20ke%20gaddaron%20ko%2C%20goli%20maaro%20saalon%20ko%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20%5Bshoot%20the%20traitors%20to%20the%20nation%5D%20and%20calling%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fvhp-rally-delhi-bjp-leaders-hate-speech-economic-boycott%5C%22%3Eeconomic%20boycott%20of%20Muslims%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20cow%20vigilantes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthree-muslims-beaten-gau-rakshaks-madhya-pradesh-seoni-beef-rumour%5C%22%3Eforcing%20their%20victims%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20shout%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EJai%20Shri%20Ram%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fbjp-leaders-fringe-anti-muslim-remarks-gulf-countries%5C%22%3E10%20Times%20When%20BJP%20Leaders%20(Not%20Fringe)%20Made%20Anti-Muslim%20Hate%20Speeches%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20often%20these%20restrictions%20on%20free%20speech%20or%20penal%20consequences%20on%20account%20of%20making%20hate%20speech%20are%20imposed%20on%20members%20or%20supporters%20of%20the%20current%20regime%20with%20reportedly%20majoritarian%20tendencies%20is%20a%20discussion%20for%20some%20other%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20relevant%20to%20note%20that%20the%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20under%20Article%2019%20(1)%20(a)%20is%20a%20multi-faceted%20freedom%2C%20and%20includes%20within%20it%20several%20aspects%20like%20the%20right%20to%20gender%20identity%20(as%20held%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F193543132%2F%5C%22%3ENALSA%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F193543132%2F%5C%22%3Ejudgement%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F193543132%2F%5C%22%3E%20(2014)%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court)%2C%20as%20also%20the%20right%20to%20%E2%80%98silence%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20interestingly%20is%20the%20converse%20of%20%E2%80%98speech%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20context%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20highlight%20the%20aspect%20of%20%E2%80%98compelled%20speech%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98forced%20speech%E2%80%99%2C%20in%20which%20the%20state%20compels%20the%20person%20to%20make%20certain%20statements%20that%20the%20person%20may%20not%20otherwise%20want%20to%20make.%20This%20forced%20speech%20is%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F921638%2F%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98must%20carry%E2%80%99%20provision%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20statute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20example%20of%20compelled%20speech%20is%20the%20statutory%20requirement%20to%20put%20disclaimers%20on%20cigarette%20packets%20that%20smoking%20is%20injurious%20to%20health%20and%20causes%20cancer.%20Such%20compelled%20speech%20cannot%20be%20a%20violation%20of%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%2C%20as%20long%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98must%20carry%E2%80%99%20provision%20furthers%20informed%20decision-making%2C%20which%20is%20considered%20the%20essence%20of%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20as%20observed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20%3Cem%3EMotion%20Picture%20Association%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1999).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scobserver.in%2Fcases%2Fkaushal-kishor-uttar-pradesh-azam-khan-freedom-of-speech-and-expression-case-background%2F%5C%22%3EKaushal%20Kishor%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scobserver.in%2Fcases%2Fkaushal-kishor-uttar-pradesh-azam-khan-freedom-of-speech-and-expression-case-background%2F%5C%22%3E(2023)%3C%2Fa%3E%20observed%20that%20if%20the%20state%20compels%20a%20citizen%20to%20carry%20out%20propaganda%20or%20a%20point%20of%20view%20contrary%20to%20their%20wish%2C%20then%20it%20may%20be%20a%20restriction%20on%20their%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%2C%20which%20must%20be%20justified%20as%20per%20Article%2019%20(2)%20of%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20in%20this%20context%20that%20the%20act%20of%20singing%20or%20standing%20for%20the%20national%20anthem%20must%20be%20viewed%2C%20in%20particular%20for%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20region.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20%E2%80%98law%E2%80%99%20mandating%20the%20citizens%20to%20sing%20or%20stand%20for%20the%20national%20anthem%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20justify%20the%20act%20of%20compelling%20citizens%20to%20sing%20or%20stand%20for%20the%20national%20anthem%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20restrictions%20under%20Article%2019%20(2).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20best%2C%20there%20is%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mha.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FNationalAnthem%2528E%2529_2.pdf%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9COrders%20Relating%20To%20The%20National%20Anthem%20Of%20India%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20issued%20by%20the%20home%20ministry%2C%20which%20states%20that%20whenever%20the%20national%20anthem%20is%20sung%20or%20played%2C%20the%20audience%20shall%20stand%20to%20attention.%20But%20interestingly%2C%20the%20same%20order%20also%20makes%20an%20exception%20that%20when%20the%20national%20anthem%20is%20played%20in%20the%20course%20of%20a%20newsreel%20or%20documentary%2C%20the%20audience%20is%20not%20expected%20to%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20event%2C%20it%20is%20debatable%20whether%20the%20said%20order%20by%20the%20home%20ministry%20can%20be%20considered%20a%20%E2%80%9Claw%E2%80%9D%20as%20understood%20in%20the%20context%20of%20Article%2019%20(2)%20of%20the%20constitution%20and%20especially%20to%20attract%20the%20penal%20provisions%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Insult%20to%20National%20Honour%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnational-anthem-forced-nationalism-iust-convocation%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Enforced%20Nationalism%E2%80%99%20Debate%20Rears%20Head%20Again%2C%20this%20Time%20at%20University%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Cem%3EShyam%20Narayan%20Chouksey%20%3C%2Fem%3E(2018)%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethe%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20its%20final%20judgement%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F81046706%2F%5C%22%3Eobserved%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20constituted%20an%20inter-ministerial%20committee%20on%20the%20playing%2Fsinging%20of%20the%20national%20anthem%20%3Cem%3Evide%3C%2Fem%3E%20an%20order%2Fnotification%20dated%20May%205%2C%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20was%20to%20give%20recommendations%20regarding%20the%20regulation%20of%20playing%2Fsinging%20the%20anthem%20and%20suggest%20changes%20in%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Insults%20to%20National%20Honour%20Act%2C%20or%20in%20the%20Orders%20Relating%20to%20the%20National%20Anthem%20of%20India%2C%20within%206%20months.%20But%20nothing%20conclusive%20has%20been%20reported%20by%20the%20said%20committee%20till%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20a%20private%20bill%2C%20i.e.%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20230712061712%2Fhttp%3A%2F164.100.47.4%2Fbillstexts%2Flsbilltexts%2Fasintroduced%2F995LS%2520As%2520Int....pdf%2520prevention%2520of%2520insults.pdf%5C%22%3EPrevention%20of%20Insults%20to%20National%20Honour%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202019%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20introduced%20by%20Parvesh%20Sahib%20Singh%2C%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20with%20the%20intention%20to%20bring%20the%20intentional%20act%20of%20disrespecting%20the%20national%20anthem%20within%20the%20purview%20of%20section%203%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Insults%20to%20National%20Honour%20Act%2C%20but%20the%20same%20did%20not%20pass%20muster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERole%20of%20dissent%20in%20a%20democracy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20essential%20component%20of%20Article%2019%20is%20the%20right%20to%20protest%20peacefully%20or%20to%20make%20one%E2%80%99s%20grievances%20known%20against%20the%20prevailing%20policies%20of%20the%20government%20in%20a%20non-violent%20manner%2C%20a%20right%20which%20assumes%20significance%20in%20any%20constitutional%20democratic%20setup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20times%2C%20sports%20personalities%20across%20the%20globe%20have%20devised%20the%20form%20of%20protest%20by%20kneeling%20or%20%E2%80%98taking%20the%20knee%E2%80%99%20while%20the%20national%20anthem%20is%20played%2C%20to%20protest%20against%20growing%20socio-economic%20or%20political%20injustices%20in%20their%20respective%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20when%20the%20NFL%20quarterback%20Colin%20Kaepernick%20started%20kneeling%20during%20the%20American%20national%20anthem%20to%20protest%20against%20racial%20injustices%20in%20the%20US%2C%20it%20evoked%20strong%20criticism%20from%20even%20the%20then-President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20in%20his%20usual%20histrionic%20outburst%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Famerican-football%2F41371179%5C%22%3Ecalled%20for%20Kaepernick%E2%80%99s%20removal%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20field%20and%20sought%20for%20him%20to%20be%20fired%20from%20the%20NFL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20singing%20or%20standing%20for%20the%20national%20anthem%20in%20protest%20is%20as%20innocuous%20an%20act%20as%20a%20peaceful%20protest%20can%20get.%20Ultimately%2C%20the%20idea%20behind%20any%20protest%20or%20dissent%20is%20to%20let%20those%20in%20power%20consider%20one%E2%80%99s%20grievances%20and%20to%20assert%20one%E2%80%99s%20legal%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20public%20speech%20in%202020%2C%20the%20current%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20Justice%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%2C%20had%20termed%C2%A0dissent%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Csafety%20valve%20of%20democracy%E2%80%9D%20and%20further%20asserted%20that%20labelling%20dissent%20as%20%E2%80%9Canti-national%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Canti-democratic%E2%80%9D%20strikes%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20deliberative%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20forthcoming%20weeks%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-article-370-kashmir-jammu%5C%22%3Eas%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20gears%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20hear%20the%20Article%20370%20abrogation%20case%2C%20the%20eventual%20verdict%20in%20the%20case%20might%20very%20well%20be%20a%20watershed%20moment%20in%20the%20chequered%20history%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20in%20trying%20to%20sincerely%20integrate%20J%26amp%3BK%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-narendra-modi-article-370%5C%22%3EArticle%20370%3A%20SC%20Rebuffs%20Modi%20Government%20in%20a%20Case%20of%20Great%20Significance%20to%20National%20Politics%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20it%20would%20also%20mark%20the%20guarantees%20of%20protection%20under%20the%20constitution%20to%20Kashmiris%20while%20attempting%20their%20integration%20with%20mainland%20India%2C%20as%20well%20a