5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhich%20films%20and%20television%20shows%20would%20be%20hit%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20walkout%20by%20actors%20would%20stop%20all%20production%20of%20film%20and%20scripted%20television%20shows%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20except%20for%20independent%20productions%20that%20are%20not%20covered%20by%20labor%20contracts%20with%20unions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProduction%20of%20popular%20series%20like%20%26quot%3BStranger%20Things%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Handmaid's%20Tale%26quot%3B%20now%20face%20lengthy%20delays.%20And%2C%20if%20strikes%20continue%2C%20major%20films%20could%20be%20postponed%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20about%20movies%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flow%20of%20films%20to%20theaters%20is%20unlikely%20to%20take%20an%20immediate%20hit%20because%20movies%20take%20two%20to%20three%20years%20to%20produce.%20But%20future%20releases%2C%20such%20as%20Marvel's%20%26quot%3BBlade%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThunderbolts%2C%26quot%3B%20have%20been%20delayed%20and%20more%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20put%20on%20hold%20until%20the%20labor%20conflicts%20are%20resolved.%20Promotional%20events%20for%20forthcoming%20movies%20still%20to%20be%20released%20will%20be%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20about%20streaming%20services%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStreaming%20services%20like%20Netflix%2C%20Amazon.com%20Inc's%20Prime%20Video%20can%20continue%20to%20supply%20local-language%20shows%20made%20in%20places%20such%20as%20Korea%20and%20India.%20But%20their%20Hollywood%20productions%20would%20be%20paused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2090%25%20of%20consumer%20spending%20on%20US%20entertainment%20industry%20goes%20to%20pay%20TV%20and%20digital%20subscriptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETom%20Cruise%2C%20Angelina%20Jolie%20among%20big%20stars%20participating%20in%20strike%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Screen%20Actors%20Guild%20(SAG-AFTRA)%20represents%20160%2C000%2