3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F101725619.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EOMG%202%2C%20Ram%20Setu%20and%20others%3A%20Akshay%20Kumar%20movies%20that%20stirred%20controversy%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Actors%20Go%20On%20Strike%20In%20New%20Blow%20To%20Struggling%20Hollywood%20Studios%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20six%20decades%2C%20Hollywood%20writers%20and%20actors%20are%20on%20strike%20at%20the%20same%20time%20-%20a%20cataclysm%20for%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20film%20and%20TV%20workers%20already%20idled%20by%20the%20entertainment%20industry's%20growing%20labor%20strife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Screen%20Actors%20Guild%2C%20which%20represents%20some%20160%2C000%20performers%2C%20announced%20a%20walkout%20Thursday%20after%20failing%20to%20reach%20a%20new%20labor%20agreement%20with%20the%20Alliance%20of%20Motion%20Picture%20%26amp%3B%20Television%20Producers%2C%20which%20represents%20studios%20including%20Walt%20Disney%20Co.%20and%20Netflix%20Inc.%20The%20strike%20begins%20at%20midnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Writers%20Guild%20of%20America%2C%20meanwhile%20has%20been%20on%20strike%20since%20May%202%2C%20shutting%20down%20late-night%20TV%20programs%20like%20The%20Tonight%20Show%2C%20halting%20many%20projects%20in%20progress%20and%20imperiling%20the%20traditional%20release%20of%20new%20broadcast%20TV%20shows%20starting%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20after%20the%20strike%20announcement%2C%20the%20studio%20alliance%20said%20the%20union%20%26quot%3Bhas%20regrettably%20chosen%20a%20path%20that%20will%20lead%20to%20financial%20hardship%20for%20countless%20thousands%20of%20people%20who%20depend%20on%20the%20industry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20studios%20say%20they%20offered%20double-digit%20percentage%20increases%20in%20salaries%20and%20higher%20pension%20and%20health%20benefits%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20boost%20in%20residuals%20-%20the%20money%20actors%20and%20others%20receive%20when%20shows%20and%20movies%20are%20rerun.%20They%20also%20offered%20protections%20against%20the%20use%20of%20actors'%20digital%20likenesses%20-%20addressing%20fears%20about%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20their%20press%20conference%2C%20SAG%20officials%20suggested%20the%20sides%20remain%20far%20apart%2C%20with%20compensation%20from%20streaming%20a%20key%20issue%20as%20online%20video%20entertainment%20takes%20predominance%20over%20broadcast%20and%20cable%20TV.%20Regarding%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20the%20union%20said%20the%20studios%20offered%20to%20pay%20background%20actors%20for%20just%20one%20day's%20work%2C%20and%20that%20their%20likenesses%20could%20then%20be%20replicated%20again%20and%20again%20in%20a%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20believe%20how%20far%20apart%20we%20are%20in%20so%20many%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Fran%20Drescher%2C%20the%20union's%20president%2C%20said%20at%20the%20conference.%20%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20business%20model%20has%20been%20changed%20by%20streaming.%20This%20is%20a%20moment%20of%20history.%20That%20is%20a%20moment%20of%20truth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWork%20on%20dozens%20of%20popular%20programs%20has%20already%20been%20halted%20including%20ABC's%20Abbott%20Elementary%20and%20Netflix's%20Stranger%20Things.%20Fox%20on%20Tuesday%20unveiled%20a%20fall%20TV%20lineup%20that%20consists%20entirely%20of%20reality%20shows%20and%20animated%20programs%20already%20completed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20the%20simultaneous%20strikes%2C%20if%20they%20last%20more%20than%20a%20few%20days%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20wider%20than%20the%20walkout%20by%20the%20writers%20alone.%20Programs%20already%20written%20could%20still%20be%20filmed%20without%20screenwriters%2C%20but%20not%20without%20actors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActors%20will%20also%20have%20to%20stop%20promoting%20upcoming%20projects%2C%20such%20as%20at%20film%20premieres%2C%20awards%20shows%20and%20events%20like%20San%20Diego%20Comi-Con%20International%2C%20scheduled%20for%20next%20week.%20Programs%20shot%20overseas%20could%20be%20impacted.%20And%20while%20other%20contracts%20may%20allow%20actors%20appearing%20in%20game%20shows%20or%20reality%20TV%20to%20continue%20working%2C%20they%20may%20get%20pressured%20to%20join%20the%20strike%20in%20sympathy%20with%20their%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMatt%20Damon%20and%20Emily%20Blunt%20had%20to%20leave%20the%20Thursday%20night%20UK%20premiere%20of%20Oppenheimer%20to%20%26quot%3Bwrite%20their%20picket%20signs%2C%26quot%3B%20director%20Christopher%20Nolan%20said%20from%20the%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJane%20Fonda%2C%20Susan%20Sarandon%2C%20Rob%20Lowe%20and%20Mark%20Ruffalo%20are%20among%20the%20stars%20who've%20already%20walked%20picket%20lines%20supporting%20the%20writers.%20Other%20unions%2C%20including%20IATSE%2C%20which%20represents%20some%20168%2C000%20stagehands%20and%20other%20entertainment%20industry%20workers%2C%20have%20put%20out%20statements%20backing%20the%20actors%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20longer%20it%20goes%2C%20it%20will%20just%20become%20a%20snowballing%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bloomberg%20Intelligence's%20Kevin%20Near.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELabor%20Unrest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20great%20Hollywood%20walkout%20is%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20battle%20that%20has%20seen%20workers%20fighting%20for%20better%20pay%20and%20benefits%20from%20businesses%20as%20far%20flung%20as%20Starbucks%20Corp.%2C%20Amazon.com%20Inc.%20and%20Delta%20Air%20Lines%20Inc.%20A%20union%20representing%20about%20340%2C000%20United%20Parcel%20Service%20Inc.%20workers%20is%20threatening%20a%20strike%20on%20Aug.%201%20if%20the%20company%20doesn't%20meet%20wage-increase%20demands%20in%20talks%20to%20renew%20a%20five-year%20labor%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entertainment%20industry%20is%20struggling%20to%20cope%20with%20two%20related%20problems%3A%20declining%20audiences%20for%20traditional%20TV%20networks%20and%20staggering%20losses%20from%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20streaming%20services%20like%20Disney%2B%20and%20Warner%20Bros.%20Discovery%20Inc.'s%20Max.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisney%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20Bob%20Iger%20on%20Thursday%20said%20the%20strike%20will%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%2C%20very%20damaging%20effect%20on%20the%20whole%20industry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20worst%20time%20in%20the%20world%20to%20add%20to%20that%20disruption%2C%26quot%3B%20Iger%20said%20in%20a%20CNBC%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20major%20entertainment%20company%20has%20fired%20staff%20in%20the%20last%2018%20months%2C%20and%20many%20of%20them%20have%20pulled%20programming%20from%20their%20streaming%20services%20to%20cut%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETragic%20Ending%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20way%2C%20the%20dual%20strikes%20mark%20a%20sad%20finale%20to%20a%20boom%20in%20film%20and%20TV%20that%20started%20when%20Netflix%20jumped%20into%20original%20production%20with%20House%20of%20Cards%20in%202013%20and%20spurred%20a%20decade%20of%20record%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20actors%20and%20writers%20say%20they've%20been%20shortchanged%20by%20the%20transition%20to%20streaming%20-%20and%20want%20to%20be%20paid%20a%20share%20of%20companies'%20earnings%20from%20shows.%20They're%20also%20seeking%20protection%20against%20the%20use%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20which%20they%20see%20as%20a%20threat%20to%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20writers%20and%20actors%20walked%20out%20together%20was%20in%201960%2C%20when%20SAG%20was%20led%20by%20Ronald%20Reagan.%20Both%20were%20fighting%20for%20revenue%20from%20movies%20that%20aired%20on%20TV%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20strike%20by%20writers%2C%20a%20100-day%20walkout%20that%20began%20in%202007%2C%20cost%20the%20California%20economy%20an%20estimated%20%242.1%20billion%20in%20lost%20output.%20The%20guild%20now%20projects%20the%20cost%20at%20%2430%20million%20a%20day%2C%20based%20on%20its%20members%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stoppage%20has%20hit%20companies%20that%20work%20with%20the%20film%20and%20TV%20industry%2C%20including%20owners%20of%20studio%20space%20like%20Hudson%20Pacific%20Properties%20Inc.%20Talent%20agencies%20have%20imposed%20layoffs%2C%20furloughs%20and%20pay%20cuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFewer%20Permits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20New%20York%2C%20home%20to%20TV%20productions%20like%20Law%20%26amp%3B%20Order%20and%20Blue%20Bloods%2C%20the%20number%20of%20permits%20to%20shoot%20films%2C%20TV%20shows%20and%20commercials%20fell%2043%25%20in%20June%20from%20their%202022%20level.%20FilmLA%2C%20which%20administers%20permits%20for%20projects%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20said%20its%20permit%20count%20was%20down%2064%25%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20July.%20No%20scripted%20TV%20series%20were%20filming%20that%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20short%20run%2C%20the%20strikes%20could%20boost%20profits%20for%20the%20media%20giants.%20With%20filming%20shut%20down%2C%20they%20won't%20have%20movie%20and%20TV%20production%20costs%20yet%20can%20continue%20to%20collect%20revenue%20from%20cable%20TV%20distributors%2C%20advertisers%20and%20program%20syndication%20sales%2C%20even%20if%20they're%20airing%20reruns%20or%20other%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20long%20as%20they%20have%20content%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20continue%20to%20make%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chris%20Thornberg%2C%20founding%20partner%20at%20Beacon%20Economics%2C%20a%20research%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20inability%20to%20commission%20and%20shoot%20new%20programming%20will%20begin%20to%20weigh%20on%20the%20industry%20in%20the%20months%20ahead.%20Media%20companies%20rely%20on%20fresh%20programming%20to%20attract%20and%20keep%20viewers%20or%20fill%20seats%20in%20movie%20theaters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStreaming%20services%20have%20already%20spaced%20out%20new%20releases%20but%20face%20a%20major%20shortfall%20in%202024%20if%20they%20can't%20get%20production%20up%20and%20running%20before%20the%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20Directors%20Guild%20of%20America%20reached%20a%20new%20contract%20last%20month%20that%20included%20a%20pay%20hike%20of%205%25%20in%20the%20first%20year%2C%20the%20writers%20and%20actors%20have%20shown%20less%20willingness%20to%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20general%2C%20labor%20is%20not%20in%20a%20mood%20to%20be%20conciliatory%20at%20this%20point%20in%20time%20given%20the%20tightness%20of%20labor%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20Beacon's%20Thornberg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689301380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Ffc11j4h8_oppenheimer-bloomberg_625x300_14_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhollywood-shuts-down-as-160-000-protest-over-wages-work-conditions-4205823%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20the%20first%20time%20in%20six%20decades%2C%20Hollywood%20writers%20and%20actors%20are%20on%20strike%20at%20the%20same%20time%20-%20a%20cataclysm%20for%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20film%20and%20TV%20workers%20already%20idled%20by%20the%20entertainment%20industry's%20growing%20labor%20strife.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhollywood-shuts-down-as-160-000-protest-over-wages-work-conditions-4205823%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhollywood-shuts-down-as-160-000-protest-over-wages-work-conditions-4205823%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhollywood-s