20is%20that%20with%20more%20users%20comes%20more%20network%20traffic%2C%20and%20T-Mobile%20prioritizes%20their%20top-paying%20customers%20over%20the%20lower-budget%20carriers%20that%20use%20their%20network%20like%20Tello%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fgoogle-fi-review%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Fi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fmint-mobile-review%5C%22%3EMint%20Mobile%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20those%20high-traffic%20instances%2C%20Tello%20users%20will%20experience%20slower%20data%20speeds%20until%20congestion%20decreases%2C%20and%20thus%20may%20be%20more%20likely%20to%20encounter%20a%202G%20connection%20rather%20than%20a%20faster%204G%20LTE%20or%205G%20one%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20their%20high-speed%20data%20allotment%20is%20not%20yet%20used%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Service%20reliability%20and%20speeds%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EService%20reliability%20and%20speeds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Tello's%20access%20to%20T-Mobile's%20expansive%20network%20means%20that%20customers%20will%20likely%20be%20covered%20throughout%20much%20of%20the%20US%2C%20your%20data%20speeds%20may%20vary%20depending%20on%20your%20location.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20own%20experience%20I%20had%20no%20issues%20sending%20and%20receiving%20texts%2C%20making%20audio%20and%20video%20calls%2C%20and%20using%20social%20media%20apps%20while%20connected%20via%204G%20LTE%20or%205G%20through%20Tello%2C%20which%20is%20a%20good%20sign%20for%20an%20MVNO%20operating%20in%20a%20major%20metropolitan%20area%20like%20New%20York.%20I%20noted%20that%20the%20audio%20quality%20of%20phone%20and%20video%20calls%20wasn't%20the%20best%20and%20would%20cut%20out%20occasionally%2C%20both%20on%20standard%20phone%20calls%20as%20well%20as%20Wi-Fi%20calls.%20However%2C%20I%20had%20no%20undelivered%20texts%20and%20no%20dropped%20calls%2C%20even%20when%20I%20only%20had%20a%20few%20bars%20of%20service%20to%20work%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20week%20of%20testing%20I%20used%20Tello's%20%26quot%3BData%26quot%3B%20plan%2C%20which%20is%20their%20option%20for%20an%20unlimited%20data%20and%20minutes%20plan.%20I%20only%20used%20about%202GB%20of%20data%20throughout%20the%20week%2C%20and%20that%20is%20far%20less%20than%20the%20plan's%2025GB%20data%20cap%20(after%20which%20my%20data%20speeds%20would%20have%20slowed%20to%202G%20rather%20than%204G%20LTE%20or%205G).%20Even%20calculating%20a%20month's%20usage%20would%20put%20me%20under%20the%20data%20cap.%20Granted%2C%20I'm%20connected%20via%20Wi-Fi%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20the%20time%20(either%20in%20the%20office%2C%20my%20home%2C%20or%20a%20cafe%2C%20all%20places%20I'm%20likely%20to%20be%20found%20working%20most%20days)%2C%20and%20if%20I'd%20relied%20solely%20on%20hotspot%20data%20my%20usage%20would%20have%20skyrocketed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20in%20mind%2C%20Tello%20customers%20can%20use%20their%20mobile%20device%20as%20a%20hotspot%20with%20no%20additional%20charge%2C%20a%20perk%20that%20many%20carriers%20will%20charge%20extra%20for.%20That%20said%2C%20your%20hotspot%20usage%20will%20come%20out%20of%20your%20monthly%20pool%20of%20data%2C%20and%20once%20you%20use%205GB%20of%20data%20through%20a%20hotspot%20your%20hotspot%20speeds%20will%20slow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20connected%20to%20my%20Tello%20hotspot%20I%20was%20able%20to%20browse%20online%20and%20watch%20YouTube%20videos%20with%20ease%2C%20but%20I%20found%20that%20it%20struggled%20to%20stream%204K%20video%20on%20Netflix%2C%20for%20instance.%20This%20wasn't%20necessarily%20a%20surprise%20to%20me%2C%20as%20I%20was%20using%20a%20hotspot%20rather%20than%20a%20stable%20Wi-Fi%20connection.%20If%20you%20rely%20on%20hotspots%20in%20your%20preferred%20places%20of%20work%20outside%20the%20home%20and%20office%20or%20if%20you%20stream%20video%20frequently%20over%20data%2C%20your%20data%20allowance%20will%20be%20spent%20quickly.%20If%20you%20only%20use%20a%20hot