robably%20wouldn't%20be%20an%20appeal%20if%20it%20was%20just%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Weissmann%2C%20an%20ex-top%20prosecutor%20in%20special%20counsel%20Robert%20Mueller's%20Russia%20investigation%2C%20also%20told%20Insider%20that%20it's%20%26quot%3Bvery%20rare%26quot%3B%20for%20%26quot%3Bthe%20government%20to%20take%20any%20appeal%2C%20particularly%20in%20sentencing%2C%20because%20the%20district%20court%20has%20an%20enormous%20discretion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeissmann%20said%20that%20the%20move%20shows%20that%20the%20DOJ%20believes%20the%20convicted%20Oath%20Keepers%20members%20committed%20an%20%26quot%3Bincredibly%20serious%20offense%26quot%3B%20that%20warrants%20harsher%20sentences%20than%20the%20ones%20handed%20down%20by%20the%20judge%20overseeing%20their%20cases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOath%20Keepers%20founder%20Elmer%20Stewart%20Rhodes%20and%20the%20other%20defendants%20were%20indicted%20on%20seditious%20conspiracy%20charges%2C%20among%20others%2C%20related%20to%20the%20deadly%202021%20Capitol%20riot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20District%20Judge%20Amit%20Mehta%20sentenced%20Rhodes%20to%2018%20years%20behind%20bars%20for%20his%20role%20in%20the%20insurrection%20%E2%80%94%20the%20most%20severe%20sentence%20to%20date%20for%20any%20of%20the%20more%20than%201%2C000%20people%20who%20have%20been%20charged%20with%20crimes%20connected%20to%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20Capitol.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Rhodes'%20case%2C%20prosecutors%20wanted%20a%20sentence%20of%2025%20years%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20defendants%20were%20also%20given%20shorter%20prison%20sentences%20than%20what%20the%20DOJ%20had%20requested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20Rhodes'%20sentence%2C%20the%20department%20also%20appealed%20the%20sentences%20of%20Kelly%20Meggs%2C%20who%20received%2012%20years%20behind%20bars%3B%20Kenneth%20Harrelson%2C%20who%20got%20four%20years%3B%20Jessica%20Watkins%2C%20who%20received%208.5%20years%3B%20Roberto%20Minuta%2C%20who%20was%20sentenced%20to%204.5%20years%3B%20Joseph%20Hackett%2C%20who%20got%203.5%20years%3B%20Edward%20Vallejo%2C%20who%20received%20three%20years%3B%20and%20David%20Moerschel%2C%20who%20was%20also%20sentenced%20to%20three%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20yet%20clear%20what%20the%20feds'%20legal%20arguments%20will%20be.%20The%20DOJ%20appeal%20filing%20didn't%20include%20details%20laying%20out%20prosecutors'%20reasoning%3B%20the%20department%20official%20told%20Insider%20those%20details%20will%20be%20laid%20out%20in%20court%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DOJ%20declined%20to%20officially%20comment%20on%20the%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20an%20attorney%20for%20Moerschel%20called%20the%20Justice%20Department's%20appeal%20%26quot%3Bridiculous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTypical%20DOJ%2C%20they%20got%20their%20pound%20of%20flesh%20and%20still%20want%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Moerschel's%20lawyer%20Scott%20Weinberg%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20wish%20they%20would%20channel%20their%20inner%20Elsa%20and%20just%20let%20it%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20Weinberg%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20Disney's%20%26quot%3BFrozen%26quot%3B%20movie.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMinuta's%20attorney%2C%20William%20Shipley%2C%20told%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20Government%20is%20legally%20entitled%20to%20appeal%20what%20it%20believes%20were%20errors%20made%20by%20the%20District%20Court%20during%20the%20sentencing%20process.%20But%20to%20the%20extent%20the%20Government%20believes%20the%20sentences%20imposed%20were%20simply%20not%20long%20enough%2C%20the%20intention%20to%20appeal%20is%20abusive%20and%20appears%20to%20be%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20continuing%20to%20advance%20its%20inaccurate%20narrative%20about%20the%20Organization%20and%20the%20individual%20defendants%20such%20as%20Mr.%20Minuta.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Government%20sought%20sentences%20as%20if%20it%20had%20prevailed%20on%20every%20charge%20it%20brought%2C%20and%20that%20all%20its%20factual%20and%20legal%20claims%20had%20been%20vindicated%20by%20the%20trials%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20simply%20false.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeggs'%20attorney%20declined%20to%20comment%2C%20and%20lawyers%20for%20Rhodes%2C%20Harrelson%2C%20Watkins%2C%20Hackett%2C%20and%20Vallejo%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20requests%20for%20comment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoj-appeal-oath-keeper-sentences-sending-a-message-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689278967000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b04f019751e300192a0541%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoj-appeal-oath-keeper-sentences-sending-a-message-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Federal%20prosecutors%20filed%20appeals%20on%20Wednesday%20for%20the%20sentences%20of%20eight%20convicted%20members%20of%20the%20far-right%20Oath%20Keepers%20group.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nmusumeci%40insider.com%20(Natalie%20Musumeci%2CSonam%20Sheth)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoj-appeal-oath-keeper-sentences-sending-a-message-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hollywood%20Shuts%20Down%20As%20Actors%20Go%20On%20Strike%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHollywood's%20actors%20announced%20Thursday%20they%20will%20go%20on%20strike%2C%20joining%20writers%20in%20the%20first%20industry-wide%20shutdown%20in%2063%20years%20after%20last-ditch%20talks%20failed%2C%20with%20nearly%20all%20film%20and%20television%20production%20set%20to%20grind%20to%20a%20halt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Screen%20Actors%20Guild%20(SAG-AFTRA)%2C%20which%20represents%20160%2C000%20performers%20including%20A-list%20stars%2C%20said%20negotiations%20had%20ended%20without%20a%20deal%20on%20their%20demands%20over%20dwindling%20pay%20and%20the%20threat%20posed%20by%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSAG-AFTRA's%20national%20board%20unanimously%20voted%20to%20issue%20a%20strike%20order%20against%20the%20studios%20and%20streamers%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20union's%20chief%20negotiator%20Duncan%20Crabtree-Ireland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20will%20begin%20at%20midnight%20Thursday%20(0700%20GMT%20Friday)%2C%20meaning%20actors%20will%20join%20writers%20on%20picket%20lines%20from%20Friday%20morning%20in%20the%20first%20Hollywood%20%26quot%3Bdouble%20strike%26quot%3B%20since%201960.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWriters%20have%20already%20spent%2011%20weeks%20on%20the%20picket%20line%2C%20after%20their%20similar%20demands%20for%20better%20pay%20and%20protections%20against%20the%20future%20use%20of%20AI%20in%20television%20and%20films%20were%20not%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPopular%20series%20set%20to%20return%20to%20television%20this%20year%20now%20face%20lengthy%20delays.%20And%2C%20if%20strikes%20continue%2C%20major%20films%20could%20be%20postponed%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20strike%20immediately%20prevents%20actors%20from%20promoting%20some%20of%20the%20year's%20biggest%20releases%2C%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20movie%20industry's%20summer%20blockbuster%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirector%20Christopher%20Nolan%20told%20the%20London%20premiere%20of%20his%20new%20film%20%26quot%3BOppenheimer%26quot%3B%20that%20his%20cast%20had%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20glitzy%20event%20in%20solidarity%20with%20the%20strike%2C%20Variety%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20A-list%20stars%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESAG-AFTRA%20represents%20everyone%20from%20A-list%20stars%20such%20as%20Meryl%20Streep%2C%20Jennifer%20Lawrence%20and%20Glenn%20Close%20to%20day%20players%20who%20do%20small%20roles%20on%20television%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vast%20majority%20of%20members%20had%20already%20voted%20to%20pre-approve%20industrial%20action%20if%20a%20deal%20was%20not%20reached.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompensation%20has%20been%20severely%20eroded%20by%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20streaming%20ecosystem.%20Furthermore%2C%20artificial%20intelligence%20poses%20an%20existential%20threat%20to%20creative%20professions%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20SAG-AFTRA%20statement%20said%20after%20the%20talks%20fell%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExecutives%20have%20%26quot%3Brefused%20to%20acknowledge%20that%20enormous%20shifts%20in%20the%20industry%20and%20economy%20have%20had%20a%20detrimental%20impact%20on%20those%20who%20perform%20labor%20for%20the%20studios%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Alliance%20of%20Motion%20Picture%20and%20Television%20Producers%2C%20which%20represents%20the%20studios%2C%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20disappointed%20that%20SAG-AFTRA%20has%20decided%20to%20walk%20away%20from%20negotiations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20union's%20choice%2C%20not%20ours%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisney%20CEO%20Bob%20Iger%20on%20Thursday%20told%20CNBC%20the%20actors'%20and%20writers'%20expectations%20were%20%26quot%3Bnot%20realistic%2C%26quot%3B%20calling%20the%20decision%20to%20strike%20%26quot%3Bvery%20disturbing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Phil%20Lord%20--%20the%20writer%2C%20director%20and%20producer%20behind%20hits%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BSpider-Man%3A%20Into%20the%20Spider-Verse%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Lego%20Movie%26quot%3B%20--%20was%20among%20those%20in%20Hollywood%20pouring%20scorn%20on%20the%20studios'%20version%20of%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAMPTP%20has%20played%20hardball%20instead%20of%20helping%20to%20solve%20entirely%20solvable%20problems%20that%20endanger%20writers%20and%20actors%20on%20the%20lower%20ends%20of%20the%20pay%20scale%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20tweeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20the%20actors'%20union%20went%20on%20strike%2C%20in%201980%2C%20it%20lasted%20more%20than%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Picket%20lines%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20writers'%20strike%20has%20already%20dramatically%20reduced%20the%20number%20of%20movies%20and%20shows%20in%20production%2C%20an%20actors'%20walkout%20shutters%20almost%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20reality%20TV%2C%20animation%20and%20talk%20shows%20could%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20New%20York%20on%20Thursday%2C%20actors%20joined%20writers%20on%20the%20picket%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20sad%20and%20it%20is%20painful%20and%20it's%20necessary%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20actress%20and%20SAG-AFTRA%20member%20Jennifer%20Van%20Dyck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20making%20so%20much%20money%2C%20and%20they%20say%20that%20we%20are%20not%20approaching%20this%20issue%20fairly....%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20go%20on%20strike%2C%20but%20there's%20just%20no%20way%20we%20can%20proceed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActors%20and%20writers%20are%20demanding%20higher%20pay%20to%20counteract%20inflation%2C%20and%20guarantees%20for%20their%20future%20livelihoods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20salaries%20when%20they%20are%20actively%20working%2C%20actors%20earn%20payments%20called%20%26quot%3Bresiduals%26quot%3B%20every%20time%20a%20film%20or%20show%20they%20starred%20in%20is%20aired%20on%20network%20or%20cable%20--%20helpful%20when%20performers%20are%20between%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20streamers%20like%20Netflix%20and%20Disney%2B%20do%20not%20disclose%20viewing%20figures%20for%20their%20shows%2C%20and%20offer%20the%20same%20flat%20rate%20for%20everything%20on%20their%20platforms%2C%20regardless%20of%20its%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuddying%20the%20waters%20further%20is%20the%20issue%20of%20AI.%20Both%20actors%20and%20writers%20want%20guarantees%20to%20regulate%20its%20use%2C%20but%20studios%20have%20refused%20to%20budge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20st