esident%20of%20Syrian%20Arab%20Republic%2C%20H.E%20Dr.%20Bashar%20al-Assad%20%26amp%3B%20exchanged%20views%20on%20strengthening%20our%20bilateral%20cooperation.%20Conveyed%20greetings%20of%20PM%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40narendramodi%3C%2Fa%3E%20ji.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHappy%20to%20have%20announced%20300%20new%20scholarships%20for%20Syrian%20students%20to%20study%20in%20India.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Ftb2b6DEqcK%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Ftb2b6DEqcK%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20V.%20Muraleedharan%20(%40MOS_MEA)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMOS_MEA%2Fstatus%2F1679477479356997632%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsana.sy%2Fen%2F%3Fp%3D312911%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Syrian%20Arab%20News%20Agency%20(SANA)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Muraleedharan%20affirmed%20that%20bilateral%20relations%20are%20constantly%20developing%20despite%20all%20circumstances.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20keen%20to%20maintain%20bilateral%20cooperation%20especially%20in%20the%20medical%20and%20educational%20sectors%2C%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20Syrian%20society%2C%20along%20with%20the%20economic%20field%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESANA%20reported%20that%20al-Assad%20affirmed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cheading%20east%20is%20one%20of%20the%20key%20principles%20on%20which%20the%20Syrian%20policy%20is%20based%E2%80%9D%2C%20not%20just%20for%20economic%20or%20political%20relations%20but%20also%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cvalues%20and%20principles%20on%20which%20the%20East%20is%20based%E2%80%9D.%20India%20is%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20the%20East%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Syrian%20president%20described%20the%20relations%20binding%20Syria%20and%20India%20as%20%E2%80%9Cdeep-rooted%E2%80%9D%20and%20hailed%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cfirm%20objective%20stances%20on%20Arab%20issues%2C%20as%20well%20as%20for%20its%20stances%20towards%20the%20war%20waged%20against%20Syria%E2%80%9D.%20He%20also%20thanked%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20assistance%20to%20the%20country%20during%20the%20deadly%20earthquake%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Asian%20states%20need%20to%20have%20good%20relations%20for%20playing%20an%20%E2%80%9Ceffective%20role%20in%20the%20new%20multipolar%20world%20order%2C%20as%20the%20only%20way%20for%20the%20West%20in%20its%20endeavours%20for%20hegemony%20is%20to%20create%20conflicts%20among%20the%20world%20countries%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20ministerial%20visit%20to%20the%20West%20Asian%20country%20since%202018%20and%20comes%20after%20Syrian%20foreign%20minister%20Fayssal%20Mekdad%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20Delhi%20last%20year.%20He%20held%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Findia-assures-to-continue-humanitarian-assistance-to-syria%2F1224519%2F%5C%22%3Emeeting%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%2C%20who%20assured%20continued%20humanitarian%20support%20to%20the%20country%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20Assad%20government%20comes%20close%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20Syria%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F5%2F7%2Farab-league-agrees-to-bring-syria-back-into-its-fold%5C%22%3Eregaining%20its%20membership%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Arab%20League%20in%20May%20this%20year.%20Its%20membership%20was%20revoked%20after%20al-Assad%20ordered%20a%20crackdown%20on%20pro-democracy%20protesters%20during%20the%20so-called%20Arab%20Spring%20in%20March%202011%2C%20which%20spiralled%20into%20a%20civil%20war%20that%20has%20killed%20nearly%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20and%20displaced%20millions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20conflict%2C%20India%20did%20not%20criticise%20the%20government%20and%20rema