406%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Athens%20is%20uncomfortably%20hot%20but%20the%20tourists%20still%20arrived%20at%20the%20Acropolis%20in%20droves.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A125%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fgreece-heatwave-people-sent-to-hospital-in-athens-as-scorching-temperatures-prompt-health-and-wildfire-fears-12920406%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fgreece-heatwave-people-sent-to-hospital-in-athens-as-scorching-temperatures-prompt-health-and-wildfire-fears-12920406%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fgreece-heatwave-people-sent-to-hospital-in-athens-as-scorching-temperatures-prompt-health-and-wildfire-fears-12920406%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Full%20Text%3A%20What%20European%20MPs%20Said%20During%20Debate%20on%20Manipur%20Violence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13175306%2FScreenshot-2023-07-13-at-5.52.20-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20European%20Parliament%20on%20Thursday%20adopted%20a%20resolution%20on%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20asking%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20protect%20religious%20minorities.%20A%20day%20earlier%2C%20the%20Members%20of%20European%20Parliament%20(MEPs)%20expressed%20their%20view%20on%20the%20violence%20and%20also%20flagged%20the%20alleged%20deterioration%20of%20human%20rights%20and%20freedoms%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.europarl.europa.eu%2Fdoceo%2Fdocument%2FRC-9-2023-0335_EN.html%5C%22%3Eresolution%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20brought%20forth%20by%20five%20parliamentary%20factions%3A%20the%20left%20Greens-European%20Free%20Alliance%2C%20the%20centre-right%20European%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party%20(EPP)%2C%20the%20centre-left%20Progressive%20Alliance%20of%20Socialists%20and%20Democrats%20(S%26amp%3BD)%2C%20the%20liberal%20Renew%20group%20and%20the%20right-wing%20European%20Conservatives%20and%20Reformists%20(ECR)%20group.%20Together%2C%20they%20account%20for%20around%2080%25%20of%20the%20MEPs%20in%20the%20705-member%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20is%20a%20transcript%20of%20the%20debate%20of%20the%20European%20parliament%E2%80%99s%20plenary%20Session%20on%20Manipur%20on%20July%2012%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChair%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20We%20can%20move%20on%20in%20the%20agenda%2C%20the%20next%20debate%20is%20on%20India%20and%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur.%20First%20of%20all%2C%20I%20give%20the%20floor%20to%20Sven%20Simon%20as%20one%20of%20the%20authors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMEP%20Sven%20Simon%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Madam%20President%20and%20colleagues.%20The%20situation%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur%20in%20the%20northeast%20of%20India%20is%20serious.%20Since%20May%2C%20in%20demonstrations%20between%20two%20population%20groups%20the%20mainly%20Hindu%20Meitei%20and%20the%20mainly%20Christian%20Kuki%2C%20over%20120%20people%20were%20killed%2C%20over%2050%2C000%20people%20are%20fleeing%2C%20over%20250%20churches%2C%20theological%20institutions%2C%20Christian%20schools%20and%20hospitals%20have%20been%20burnt%20down%20without%20the%20perpetrators%20being%20prevented%20by%20the%20local%20authorities.%20We%20call%20on%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20do%20everything%20to%20restore%20order%2C%20to%20bring%20the%20perpetrators%20to%20Justice%2C%20and%20to%20stop%20excessive%20violence.%20We%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20like%20to%20wag%20fingers%20at%20anybody%20from%20here%2C%20but%20with%20this%20resolution%20from%20the%20European%20Parliament%2C%20we%20call%20on%20the%20most%20populous%20democracy%20to%20do%20what%20it%20is%20duty-bound%20to%20do%20in%20its%20Constitution%3A%20to%20maintain%20religious%20freedom%20also%20for%20Christians%20in%20Manipur.%20One%20thing%2C%20colleagues%2C%20has%20irritated%20me%20with%20the%20negotiations%20with%20other%20groups.%20How%20difficult%20it%20is%20for%20the%20Greens%20and%20colleagues%20and%20those%20on%20the%20Left%20to%20say%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20Christians%20who%20are%20affected.%20They%20wriggle%20with%20platitudes%20about%20discrimination%20and%20religious%20intolerance%20and%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20state%20what%20is%20obvious%20%E2%80%93%20persecutions%20of%20Christians%20are%20real%2C%20and%20it%20is%20our%20duty%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20they%20stop%2C%20also%20in%20Manipur.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChair%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%2C%20Mr%20Zeman.%20Pierre%20Larrouturou%20is%20the%20next%20speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMEP%20Pierre%20Larrouturou%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EFriends%2C%20in%20Manipur%20in%20Northeast%20India%2C%20violence%20has%20claimed%20more%20than%20120%20victims%20over%20two%20months.%20120%20people%20killed%2C%201%2C700%20houses%20have%20been%20destroyed%2C%20250%20churches%20%E2%80%93%20not%20just%20one%20or%20two%20churches%2C%20250%20churches%20%E2%80%93%20and%2040%20000%20people%20are%20displaced%20because%20they%E2%80%99ve%20run%20away%20from%20the%20violence%20to%20save%20their%20skins.%20This%20is%20a%20dramatic%20situation%2C%20we%20have%20to%20do%20everything%20possible%20to%20end%20violence.%20Since%20he%20entered%20power%20in%202014%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20has%20been%20implementing%20a%20radical%20nationalist%20Hindu%20policy%20which%20has%20had%20terrible%20consequences%20%5Bfor%5D%20journalists%2C%20religious%20minorities%2C%20and%20human%20rights%20fighters.%20He%20always%20says%20that%20he%20is%20an%20heir%20to%20Mahatma%20Gandhi.%20We%20all%20admire%20%5Bhim%2C%5D%20he%20takes%20meditation%20time%2C%20he%20created%20a%20world%20yoga%20day.%20He%20seems%20kind%20and%20well-meaning.%20But%20in%20India%2C%20millions%20of%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20suffer%20every%20single%20day%20because%20the%20government%20violates%20their%20most%20fundamental%20rights.%20The%20situation%20is%20serious.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20the%20European%20Parliament%20must%20vote%20tomorrow%20on%20a%20very%20clear%20resolution.%20It%20has%20to%20be%20clear%20in%20denouncing%20the%20nationalist%20discourse%20of%20Mr%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20to%20fully%20respect%20fundamental%20freedoms%2C%20freedom%20of%20expression%2C%20and%20religious%20freedoms%20for%20everyone.%20The%20resolution%20has%20to%20call%20for%20the%20violence%20to%20end%20immediately%20and%20to%20authorise%20humanitarian%20aid%20%5Bin%5D%20the%20presence%20of%20observers%20and%20journalists%20wherever%20necessary.%20They%20have%20to%20accept%20democratic%20functioning%2C%20no%20longer%20criminalise%20anyone%20who%20criticises%20government%20policy.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20democracy%20is%20about.%20The%20number%20of%20NGOs%20that%20are%20authorised%20to%20operate%20in%20India%20has%20been%20cut%20by%20three%20%5Btimes%5D%20in%20just%20a%20few%20years.%20They%20are%20trying%20to%20suffocate%20the%20NGOs%2C%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20suffocate%20democracy%20in%20civil%20society.%20There%20is%20no%20economic%20development%20without%20democracy.%20The%20European%20Parliament%20has%20to%20demand%20that%20respect%20for%20human%20rights%20is%20fully%20included%20in%20the%20EU-India%20partnership%2C%20including%20trade%20relations.%20That%20is%20in%20black%20and%20white%20in%20our%20text.%20We%20need%20to%20ensure%20that%20all%20our%20leaders%20talk%20about%20human%20rights%20when%20they%20visit%20India%2C%20publicly%20and%20systematically.%20Nobody%20is%20proposing%20breaking%20off%20relations%20with%20India.%20It%20is%20a%20great%20democracy%20but%20it%20has%20to%20be%20a%20better%20democracy%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20support%20dialogue%20between%20India%20and%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChair%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you.%20The%20next%20author%20on%20our%20list%20is%20Madame%20Alviina%20Alamets%C3%A4.%20One%20and%20a%20half%20minutes.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMEP%20Alviina%20Alamets%C3%A4%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Honourable%20chair%20and%20colleagues.%20My%20deepest%20condolences%20to%20the%20families%20of%20the%20140%20people%20that%20have%20died%20in%20Manipur.%20This%20violence%20has%20led%20to%20the%20displacement%20of%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20and%20I%20think%20that%20the%20Indian%20authorities%20must%20take%20action.%20There%20cannot%20be%20any%20more%20victims.%20Access%20to%20humanitarian%20aid%20and%20impartial%20observers%20to%20the%20area%20must%20be%20allowed.%20We%20should%20all%20be%20worried%20about%20the%20worsening%20human%20rights%20situation%20in%20India.%20Freedom%20of%20press%20has%20narrowed.%20Journalists%20and%20activists%20have%20been%20arrested%20for%20false%20reasons.%20Discrimination%20and%20hate%20have%20increased.%20And%20this%20is%20also%20what%20I%20saw%20personally%20when%20I%20visited%20India%20in%20December%20%5B2022%5D.%20This%20saddens%20me%20as%20India%20is%20a%20very%20important%20partner%20for%20us.%20Even%20India%20has%20to%20make%20human%20rights%20and%20democracy%20a%20fundamental%20part%20of%20their%20partnership%20in%20all%20regards%2C%20including%20trade.%20The%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20needs%20all%20of%20us%20to%20commit%20to%20open%2C%20transparent%2C%20and%20accountable%20ways%20to%20address%20conflict%20peacefully.%20The%20goal%20must%20be%20to%20end%20this%20violence%20and%20to%20bring%20about%20a%20peaceful%20resolution%20for%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20and%20for%20India%20to%20truly%20address%20all%20the%20root%20causes%20that%20are%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20these%20conflicts.%20I%20thank%20you%2C%20my%20colleagues%2C%20for%20cooperating%20on%20this%20and%20I%20send%20my%20deepest%20condolences%20to%20those%20who%20are%20suffering%20because%20of%20the%20human%20rights%20situation%20and%20the%20violence.%20Thank%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChair%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%20and%20now%20I%20give%20the%20floor%20to%20the%20next%20author%2C%20Mr%20Bert-Jan%20Ruissen%20for%20one%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMEP%20Bert-Jan%20Ruissen%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%2C%20president%2C%20commissioner%2C%20honourable%20members.%20When%20we%20discuss%20India%2C%20often%20we%20are%20talking%20about%20trade%20opportunities.%20Unfortunately%2C%20today%20we%E2%80%99re%20here%20to%20talk%20about%20human%20rights%2C%20about%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur%2C%20where%20we%20have%20seen%20ethnic%20clashes%20taking%20on%20an%20increasing%20religious%20dimension.%20The%20events%20of%20the%20last%2010%20weeks%20are%20tragic.%20120%20lives%20lost%2C%2050%2C000%20people%20displaced%2C%20250%20churches%20destroyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20this%20is%20not%20an%20isolated%20incident.%20Across%20India%2C%20those%20who%20are%20not%20Hindu%2C%20in%20particular%20Christians%2C%20are%20facing%20growing%20intolerance%2C%20violence%2C%20humiliation%2C%20discrimination.%20We%E2%80%99re%20seeing%20this%20in%20anti-conversion%20laws%20in%20different%20federal%20states.%20Our%20joint%20resolution%20is%20crystal%20clear%20%E2%80%93%20we%20are%20calling%20on%20India%20to%20do%20everything%20within%20its%20power%20to%20end%20ethnic%20and%20religious%20violence%2C%20to%20punish%20perpetrators%2C%20and%20end%20Hindu%20extremism.%20Without%20iron-clad%20guarantees%20in%20this%20area%2C%20we%20cannot%20talk%20about%20a%20new%20trade%20agreement%20with%20India.%20Thank%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChair%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%20and%20now%20I%20give%20the%20floor%20to%20the%20next%20author%2C%20Mr%20Miguel%20Urb%C3%A1n%20Crespo%20for%20one%20minute.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMEP%20Miguel%20Urb%C3%A1n%20Crespo%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%20very%20much%2C%20president.%20Ethnic%20minorities%20and%20religious%20minorities%20in%20India%20are%20systematically%20discriminated%20against.%20They%20are%20stigmatised%20and%20persecuted%20by%20the%20extreme%20right%20of%20Modi.%20This%20same%20applies%20to%20those%20who%20level%20criticism%20at%20the%20government.%20There%20are%20dozens%20of%20human%20rights%20defenders%20who%E2%80%99ve%20been%20put%20in%20prison%2C%20even%20though%20this%20parliament%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20mentioned%20them.%20What%20happens%20in%20Manipur%20is%20also%20the%20upshot%20of%20the%20xenophobic%20policies%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20the%20very%20same%20government%20which%20issues%20veiled%20threats%20so%20that%20the%20kinds%20of%20debates%20we%20are%20having%20do%20not%20occur.%20Now%2C%20enough%20silent%20diplomacy.%20We%20must%20outright%20condemn%20the%20systematic%20abuses%20perpetrated%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20and%20we%20must%20clamour%20for%20the%20release%20of%20all%20political%20prisoners.%20Trade%20relations%20are%20political%20relations%20and%20must%20be%20tied%20to%20compliance%20with%20human%20rights.%20It%E2%80%99s%20high%20time%20to%20send%20a%20crystal%20clear%20message%20of%20support%20for%20the%20Indian%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChair%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%2C%20and%20now%20I%20give%20the%20floor%20to%20our%20next%20speaker%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20EPP%2C%20Madame%20Michaela%20%C5%A0ojdrov%C3%A1%20for%20one%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMEP%20Michaela%20%C5%A0ojdrov%C3%A1%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%2C%20dear%20colleagues%2C%20Commissioner.%20The%20recent%20violent%20clashes%20between%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20have%20caused%20widespread%20devastation.%20Over%2050%2C000%20people%2C%20including%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20Christians%2C%20have%20been%20displaced%20and%20lives%20have%20been%20lost.%20Numerous%20religious%20symbols%20and%20places%20of%20worship%20have%20been%20targeted%20with%20more%20than%20220%20churches%20burnt%20or%20damaged.%20We%20urge%20Indian%20authorities%20to%20take%20immediate%20action%20to%20stop%20the%20violence%20and%20protect%20religious%20minorities%20%E2%80%93%20particularly%20the%20Christian%20community%20in%20Manipur.%20We%20call%20on%20all%20sides%20to%20exercise%20restraint%2C%20and%20for%20political%20leaders%20to%20refrain%20from%20making%20inflammatory%20statements.%20They%20should%20impartially%20mediate%20tensions%20and%20reject%20any%20nationalistic%20rhetoric.%20Today%2C%20let%20us%20send%20a%20clear%20message%3A%20the%20EU%20holds%20a%20powerful%20tool%20in%20trade%20policy%2C%20and%20we%20demand%20the%20integration%20of%20human%20rights%20into%20our%20EU-India%20partnership.%20We%20also%20urge%20the%20reinforcement%20of%20EU-India%20human%20rights%20dialogue.%20Thank%20you%20for%20your%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChair%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%2C%20and%20now%20I%20give%20the%20floor%20to%20the%20representative%20of%20the%20Green%20Alliance%2C%20Mr%20B%C3%BCtikofer%20for%20one%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMEP%20Reinhard%20B%C3%BCtikofer%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Assistant%20commissioner%2C%20colleagues.%20This%20human%20rights%20urgency%20should%20not%20be%20used%20as%20an%20occasion%20to%20insult%20India%20or%20to%20voice%20threats%20with%20regards%20to%20the%20trade%20negotiations%20that%20we%E2%80%99re%20trying%20to%20bring%20to%20a%20successful%20end%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20This%20is%20about%20specific%20human%20rights%20issues%20and%20I%20think%20it%20is%20right%20to%20say%20that%20we%20have%20common%20ground%20with%20India%20in%20that%20regard%20and%20that%20we%20should%20reinforce%20as%20the%20resolution%20says%2C%20the%20EU-India%20human%20rights%20dialogue%2C%20And%20in%20particular%2C%20I%20would%20underscore%20the%20sentence%20that%20says%20%E2%80%98there%20should%20be%20regular%20dialogue%20organised%20between%20the%20European%20Parliament%20and%20the%20Parliament%20of%20India.%E2%80%99%20My%20colleague%2C%20Simon%2C%20has%20said%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20wag%20his%20finger%20at%20India.%20He%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20do%20without%20wagging%20though%2C%20so%20he%20wagged%20his%20finger%20at%20the%20Greens.%20I%20will%20not%20retaliate.%20I%20will%20just%20say%2C%20we%20will%20defend%20religious%20freedom%20wherever%20it%20is%20endangered%2C%20be%20it%20Christians%20or%20otherwise.%20Thank%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChair%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%20and%20now%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20ECR%20group%2C%20Mr%20Adam%20Bielan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMEP%20Adam%20Bielan%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%20very%20much%2C%20Mr%20President.%20The%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20is%20deeply%20concerning.%20Since%20May%2C%20tensions%20between%20the%20mainly%20Hindu%20Meitei%20and%20mainly%20Christian%20Kuki%20communities%20have%20escalated%20to%20the%20most%20violent%20clashes%20in%20decades.%20Over%20140%20people%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%2C%20tens%20of%20thousands%20are%20displaced%2C%20and%20private%20and%20public%20property%20has%20been%20destroyed.%20Despite%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20authorities%20are%20not%20taking%20sufficient%20action%20and%20fostering%20peace%20dialogues.%20While%20the%20Manipur%20Tribal%20Forum%E2%80%99s%20plea%20for%20protection%20of%20the%20Kuki%20tribe%20by%20the%20Indian%20army%20has%20been%20rejected%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20We%2C%20therefore%2C%20urge%20all%20parties%20to%20cease%20hostilities%20and%20resolve%20the%20underlying%20regional%20and%20religious%20issues.%20The%20EU%20and%20its%20member%20states%20should%20collaborate%20with%20like-minded%20countries%20and%20organisations%20to%20assess%20possible%20further%20steps%20and%20continue%20to%20raise%20human%20rights%2C%20and%20especially%20religious%20freedom%2C%20concerns%20with%20the%20Indian%20authorities.%20Thank%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChair%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%2C%20and%20now%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20EPP%20group%2C%20Mr%20Ji%C5%99%C3%AD%20Posp%C3%AD%C5%A1il%20for%20one%20minute.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMEP%20Ji%C5%99%C3%AD%20Posp%C3%AD%C5%A1il%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EThank%20you%2C%20Mr%20President.%20Like%20my%20colleagues%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20support%20the%20draft%20resolution%20that%2C%20in%20my%20view%2C%20very%20much%20goes%20to%20the%20point.%20It%E2%80%99s%20up%20to%20date.%20India%20is%20the%20largest%20democracy%20in%20the%20world%2C%20a%20key%20partner%20of%20the%20EU%20in%20business.%20Democracy%20in%20recent%20years%20has%20worked%20in%20India%2C%20but%20democracy%20is%20also%20about%20human%20rights%20protection%2C%20and%20certainly%20there%20have%20been%20cases%20where%20human%20rights%20failed%20to%20be%20protected%2C%20especially%20those%20of%20religious%20minorities.%20We%20mentioned%20the%20Christian%20religious%20minority%20in%20the%20resolution%2C%20not%20only%20in%20one%20federal%20state%20of%20India%20but%20throughout%20the%20whole%20country.%20We%20must%20appeal%20to%20the%20central%20Indian%20government%2C%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20impossible%20that%20a%20key%20partner%20of%20the%20EU%20not%20guarantee%20key%20human%20rights%20of%20anybody%2C%20whether%20they%20are%20of%20Christian%20religion%20or%20anybody%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChair%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%2C%20and%20now%20I%20give%20the%20floor%20to%20Mr%20Il%C4%8Di%C4%87%20for%20one%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMEP%20Ladislav%20Il%C4%8Di%C4%87%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Ladies%20and%20gentlemen.%20Although%20dramatic%20violence%20in%20India%20in%20Manipur%20began%20because%20of%20land%20ownership%2C%20it%20seems%20that%20very%20quickly%20it%20also%20became%20religiously%20conditioned%20violence.%20Over%20250%20churches%20were%20attacked%2C%20numerous%20cemeteries%20and%20parish%20houses.%20India%20is%20an%20important%20partner%20to%20the%20European%20Union.%20But%20if%20we%20as%20a%20Christian%20community%20can%20respect%20other%20faiths%20and%20identities%2C%20we%20must%20ask%20our%20partners%20to%20do%20the%20same.%20I%20propose%20an%20urgent%20visit%20by%20the%20European%20Special%20Envoy%20for%20Religious%20Freedoms%20to%20India.%20And%20the%20way%20the%20Indian%20government%20will%20treat%20this%20proposal%20will%20show%20whether%20the%20authorities%20there%20are%20for%20the%20time%20being%20only%20powerless%20in%20such%20cases%2C%20or%20whether%20they%20knowingly%20allow%20the%20persecution%20of%20religious%20minorities%20by%20radical%20groups.%20Our%20message%20must%20be%20clear%20we%20will%20not%20turn%20our%20heads%20away%20from%20violence%20and%20we%20will%20not%20turn%20our%20backs%20on%20persecuted%20Christians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChair%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%2C%20and%20now%20I%20give%20the%20floor%20to%20Madame%20Miriam%20Lexmann%20for%20one%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMEP%20Miriam%20Lexmann%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%20chair%2C%20colleagues.%20The%20state%20of%20freedom%20of%20religion%20and%20belief%20in%20a%20society%20is%20an%20important%20litmus%20test%20to%20the%20state%20of%20other%20fundamental%20freedoms.%20Therefore%2C%20while%20Indian%20officials%20often%20like%20to%20boast%20that%20the%20country%20is%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20democracy%2C%20intolerance%20and%20violence%20against%20religious%20minorities%20paint%20a%20different%20picture.%20In%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur%20at%20least%20100%20people%20are%20dead%2C%20tens%20of%20thousands%20displaced%2C%20hundreds%20of%20houses%20belonging%20to%20Christians%20destroyed%2C%20along%20with%20250%20churches%2C%20theological%20institutions%2C%20schools%20and%20hospitals%2C%20as%20well%20as%20several%20temples.%20These%20attacks%20against%20Christians%20are%20not%20isolated%20incidents.%20They%20are%20organised%2C%20leaving%20behind%20destruction%20and%20shattered%20lives.%20The%20EU%20cannot%20close%20its%20eyes%20to%20these%20crimes.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20call%20on%20our%20Special%20Envoy%20for%20Freedom%20of%20Religion%20and%20the%20EES%20to%20communicate%20clearly%20to%20the%20Indian%20authorities%20the%20need%20to%20stop%20this%20violence%20and%20to%20provide%20the%20necessary%20support%20to%20the%20victims%20immediately.%20Thank%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChair%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%20very%20much%2C%20now%20colleagues%20start%20the%20%5Bunclear%5D%20procedure.%20I%20have%20one%20speaker%20on%20the%20%5Bunclear%5D%20procedure%2C%20and%20I%20will%20give%20a%20floor%20to%20Eugen%20Tomac.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMEP%20Eugen%20Tomac%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%20very%20much.%20We%20do%20have%20to%20show%20our%20solidarity%20to%20people%20who%20find%20themselves%20in%20such%20a%20difficult%20situation.%20What%20is%20happening%20in%20Manipur%20is%20reflecting%20the%20reality%20that%20very%20often%20member%20states%20won%E2%80%99t%20look%20at%2C%20and%20won%E2%80%99t%20look%20at%20in%20depth%20and%20I%20think%20the%20European%20Commission%20has%20the%20obligation%20now%20to%20act%20more%20strongly%20in%20its%20relations%20with%20the%20Indian%20government.%20They%20have%20to%20ask%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20protect%20all%20Indian%20citizens%2C%20including%20Christians%20because%20more%20than%2050%2C000%20Indians%20are%20displaced%2C%20more%20than%20250%20churches%20have%20been%20destroyed%2C%20and%20all%20of%20this%20does%20mean%20that%20the%20European%20Commission%20has%20to%20act%20they%20have%20to%20act%20to%20protect.%20It%20is%20not%20the%20fault%20of%20these%20people%20that%20the%20Government%20is%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20protect%20the%20Constitution.%20Thank%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECommissioner%20Mairead%20McGuinness%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%20President%2C%20Honourable%20Members.%20I%20really%20would%20like%20to%20reassure%20you%20that%20the%20European%20Union%20is%20following%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur%20closely%2C%20and%20we%20are%20very%20saddened%2C%20deeply%20saddened%2C%20by%20the%20large%20number%20of%20deaths%20and%20of%20injured%20and%20displaced%20persons%20since%20violence%20erupted%20in%20Manipur%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20May.%20The%20Indian%20authorities%20have%20taken%20a%20number%20of%20measures%20to%20address%20this%20very%20tense%20situation.%20A%20commission%20of%20inquiry%20has%20been%20set%20up%20to%20investigate%20instance%20of%20violence.%20A%20peace%20committee%20has%20been%20established%20with%20broad%20participation%20to%20facilitate%20peace%20negotiations%20and%20dialogue%20between%20the%20conflicting%20groups.%20We%20hope%20that%20these%20measures%20will%20very%20soon%20bring%20results%20so%20that%20this%20wave%20of%20violence%20and%20the%20profound%20mistrust%20between%20the%20communities%20comes%20to%20an%20end.%20India%20is%20a%20strategic%20partner%20of%20the%20EU.%20Our%20relations%20are%20based%20on%20mutual%20respect%2C%20and%20the%20protection%20and%20promotion%20of%20Human%20Rights%20and%20fundamental%20freedoms%20are%20at%20the%20core%20of%20our%20partnership.%20We%20discuss%20regularly%20with%20India%20the%20challenges%20and%20best%20approaches%20on%20human%20rights%20in%20both%20Europe%20and%20India.%20The%20annual%20EU-India%20Human%20Rights%20dialogue%20provides%20a%20good%20platform%20for%20frank%20and%20open%20discussion%20between%20us.%20The%20last%20meeting%20took%20place%20in%20July%20of%20last%20year%2C%20and%20the%20next%20one%20should%20happen%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%20The%20EU%20is%20ready%20to%20support%20our%20Indian%20friends%20if%20requested%20in%20their%20efforts%20towards%20rebuilding%20peace%20and%20trust%20between%20the%20different%20groups%20in%20Manipur.%20Thank%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689252013000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13175306%2FScreenshot-2023-07-13-at-5.52.20-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Ffull-text-european-mp-debate-manipur-violence%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20European%20Parliament%20on%20Thursday%20adopted%20a%20resolution%20that%20called%20on%20Indian%20authorities%20to%20take%20%E2%80%9Call%20necessary%E2%80%9D%20measures%20to%20stop%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20and%20protect%20religious%20minorities%2C%20especially%20Christians.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Ffull-text-european-mp-debate-manipur-violence%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20Accuses%20Centre%20of%20'Usurping'%20Publicity%20Funds%20of%20Ministries%20for%20Own%20Use%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13173545%2F1200px-Jairam_Ramesh_New_Delhi_09-2012.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20accused%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20of%20%E2%80%9Cundermining%20the%20sanctity%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Budget%20by%20%E2%80%9Cusurping%E2%80%9D%2040%25%20of%20funds%20allocated%20to%20various%20ministries%20for%20publicity%20and%20handing%20it%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Communication%20(CBC).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESharing%20an%20order%20by%20the%20finance%20ministry%20dated%C2%A0%20May%2019%2C%202023%2C%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20general%20secretary%20and%20media%20and%20communications%20in-charge%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%20that%20under%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20the%20central%20government%20has%20become%20a%20%E2%80%9CCentral(ised)%20Propaganda%20Machine.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20copy%20of%20the%20order%20posted%20on%20Twitter%20by%20the%20Congress%20and%20shared%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20states%3A%20%E2%80%9CFor%20effective%20dissemination%20of%20information%20about%20government%20policies%20and%20programmes%2C%20in%20the%20most%20cost-effective%20manner%2C%20it%20has%20been%20decided%20to%20place%2040%25of%20the%20budget%20allocation%202023-24%20of%20Ministries%2FDepartments%2FOrganisations%20(as%20per%20list%20attached)%20under%20the%20object%20head%20Advertising%20and%20Publicity%20at%20the%20disposal%20of%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Communications%20(CBC)%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%2C%20with%20immediate%20effect.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20paragraph%202%2C%20the%20order%20states%20that%20%E2%80%9CFinancial%20Advisers%20of%20Ministries%2FDepartments%20concerned%20are%20requested%20to%20issue%20LoA%20(Letter%20of%20Authorisation)%20in%20favour%20of%20M%2Fo%20I%26amp%3BB%20authorising%20it%20to%20operate%20relevant%20budget%20heads%20in%20their%20demand%20to%20settle%20bills%20raised%20on%20account%20of%20their%20advertisement%20and%20publicity%20campaign%2C%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20amount%20mentioned%20in%20LoA%20(details%20attached).%20It%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20amount%20allocated%20through%20LoA%20will%20not%20be%20available%20for%20expenditure%2Fre-appropriation%20by%20the%20functional%20Ministry%2FDepartment%20in%20the%20current%20FY%202023-24.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20CBC%E2%80%99s%20Budget%20for%202023-24%20approved%20by%20Parliament%20is%20Rs%20200%20crore.%20With%20the%20May%2019th%2C%202023%20order%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%20the%20Budget%20for%20CBC%20for%20the%20current%20year%20will%20suddenly%20zoom%20to%20more%20than%20Rs%20750%20crores%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ramesh%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EParliament%20votes%20Budgets%20for%20all%20Departments%20and%20Ministries%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20Each%20programme%2Fscheme%20has%20a%20distinct%20Budget%20Head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20on%20May%2019%2C%202023%20in%20an%20unprecedented%20move%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%20has%20ordered%20that%2040%25%20of%20the%20funds%20voted%20by%20Parliament%20for%20%E2%80%98Advertising%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FYusTFtx52R%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FYusTFtx52R%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20(%40Jairam_Ramesh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1679355833711296513%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20money%20will%20be%20used%20by%20the%20CBC%20for%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%202024%20general%20election%20campaign.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20the%20CBC%2C%20along%20with%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20and%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20be%20the%20spearhead%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%202024%20election%20campaign.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAsking%20if%20this%20is%20not%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ede%20facto%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20misappropriation%E2%80%9D%20of%20funds%2C%20Ramesh%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20prime%20minister%20by%20calling%20him%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPrachar%20Mantri%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(broadcasting%20minister).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20propaganda%20machine%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20enough%20funds.%20Now%20with%20this%20surgical%20strike%2C%20just%20like%20the%2040%25%20Commission%20Sarkara%20dislodged%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20Modi%20Govt.%20usurps%2040%25%20of%20funds%20already%20allocated%20to%20ministries%20by%20Parliament%20and%20enriches%20the%20CBC%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ramesh%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20order%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfurther%20subversion%20of%20Parliament%E2%80%99s%20Constitutional%20obligations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20undermined%20the%20expertise%20of%20specific%20ministries%20as%20well%20as%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20budget%20voted%20by%20the%20Parliament.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EForm