C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.europarl.europa.eu%2Fdoceo%2Fdocument%2FRC-9-2023-0335_EN.html%5C%22%3Eresolution%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20tabled%20by%20five%20political%20groups%20and%20adopted%20by%20a%20show%20of%20hands%20during%20the%20plenary%20session%20of%20the%20European%20Parliament.%20The%20adoption%20took%20place%20in%20the%20afternoon%20along%20with%20other%20votes%20on%20schedule%2C%20just%20after%20the%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20landed%20in%20France%20for%20an%20official%20visit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSuch%20interference%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20internal%20affairs%20is%20unacceptable%2C%20and%20reflects%20a%20colonial%20mindset%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndian%20authorities%20at%20all%20levels%2C%20including%20the%20judiciary%2C%20are%20seized%20of%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20and%20are%20taking%20steps%20to%20maintain%20peace%20and%20harmony%20and%20law%20and%20order.%20The%20European%20Parliament%20would%20be%20well%20advised%20to%20utilize%20its%20time%20more%20productively%20on%20its%20internal%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20day%20earlier%2C%20Indian%20foreign%20secretary%20Vinay%20Kwatra%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Feuropean-parliament-manipur-narendra-modi%5C%22%3Etold%20reporters%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20this%20was%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinternal%20matter%E2%80%9D.%20He%20had%20also%20indicated%20that%20India%20had%20reached%20out%20to%20EU%20lawmakers%20on%20this%20issue%20ahead%20of%20the%20tabling%20of%20the%20resolution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20five%20parliamentary%20factions%20that%20authored%20the%20resolution%20were%20the%20left%20Greens-European%20Free%20Alliance%2C%20the%20centre-right%20European%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party%20(EPP)%2C%20the%20centre-left%20Progressive%20Alliance%20of%20Socialists%20and%20Democrats%20(S%26amp%3BD)%2C%20the%20liberal%20Renew%20group%20and%20the%20right-wing%20European%20Conservatives%20and%20Reformists%20(ECR)%20group.%20They%20account%20for%20around%2080%25%20of%20the%20lawmakers%20in%20the%20705-member%20parliament.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20resolution%20expressed%20concern%20that%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20over%20the%20last%20two%20months%20has%20left%20over%20120%20dead%2C%20with%2050%2C000%20displaced%20and%20destroyed%201%2C700%20houses%2C%20over%20250%20churches%20and%20several%20temples.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20resolution%20called%20on%20India%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctake%20all%20necessary%20measures%20and%20make%20the%20utmost%20effort%20to%20promptly%20halt%20the%20ongoing%20ethnic%20and%20religious%20violence%2C%20to%20protect%20all%20religious%20minorities%2C%20such%20as%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Christian%20community%2C%20and%20to%20pre-empt%20any%20further%20escalation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20also%20urged%20political%20leaders%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccease%20inflammatory%20statements%2C%20re-establish%20trust%20and%20play%20an%20impartial%20role%20in%20mediating%20the%20tensions%E2%80%9D.%20The%20European%20Parliament%20also%20asserted%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthose%20who%20are%20critical%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20conduct%20not%20be%20criminalised%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20European%20Parliament%20also%20noted%20the%20violence%20had%20been%20instigated%20by%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Epolitically%20motivated%2C%20divisive%20policies%20promoting%20Hindu%20majoritarianism%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20well%20as%2C%20increased%20activity%20by%20militant%20groups.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20observed%20that%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eaccounts%20of%20partisan%20involvement%20by%20security%20forces%20in%20the%20killings%20have%20increased%20distrust%20in%20the%20authorities%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20European%20lawmakers%20asserted%20that%20human%20rights%20should%20be%20an%20important%20part%20of%20ongoing%20negotiations%20between%20India%20and%20the%20EU%20on%20the%20free%20trade%20agreement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20during%20the%20debate%20over%20the%20resolution%2C%20Sven%20Simon%20from%20the%20largest%20EPP%20group%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20like%20to%20wag%20fingers%20at%20anybody%20from%20here%2C%20but%20with%20this%20resolution%20from%20the%20European%20Parliament%2C%20we%20call%20on%20the%20most%20populous%20democracy%20to%20do%20what%20it%20is%20duty%20bound%20to%20do%20in%20its%20Constitution%20to%20maintain%20religious%20freedom%2C%20also%20for%20Christians%20in%20Manipur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F1utpajf4PJU%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20ECR%20group%2C%20Bert-Jan%20Ruissen%20asserted%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20joint%20resolution%20is%20crystal%20clear%20%E2%80%93%20we%20are%20calling%20on%20India%20to%20do%20everything%20within%20its%20power%20to%20end%20ethnic%20and%20religious%20violence%2C%20to%20punish%20perpetrators%2C%20and%20end%20Hindu%20extremism.%20Without%20ironclad%20guarantees%20in%20this%20area%2C%20we%20cannot%20talk%20about%20a%20new%20trade%20agreement%20with%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20EU%20Commissioner%20Mairead%20McGuinness%20told%20the%20lawmakers%20that%20the%20European%20Union%20was%20%E2%80%9Cfollowing%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur%20closely%2C%20and%20we%20are%20very%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esaddened%2C%20deeply%20saddened%2C%20by%20the%20large%20number%20of%20deaths%20and%20of%20injured%20and%20displaced%20persons%20since%20violence%20erupted%20in%20Manipur%20at%20the%20beginning%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eof%20May%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStating%20that%20the%20EU%20is%20%E2%80%9Cready%20to%20support%E2%80%9D%20India%20%E2%80%9Cif%20requested%20in%20their%20efforts%20towards%20rebuilding%20peace%20and%20trust%20between%20the%20different%20groups%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%9D%2C%20McGuinness%20recounted%20some%20steps%20taken%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20like%20setting%20up%20a%20commission%20of%20inquiry%20and%20a%20peace%20committee.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20hope%20that%20these%20measures%20will%20very%20soon%20bring%20results%20so%20that%20this%20wave%20of%20violence%20and%20the%20profound%20mistrust%20between%20the%20communities%20comes%20to%20an%20end%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENoting%20that%20India%20and%20the%20EU%20were%20strategic%20partners%2C%20the%20EU%20commissioner%20said%20that%20both%20sides%20regularly%20discuss%20human%20rights%20challenges%20in%20both%20regions%2C%20especially%20in%20%E2%80%9Cfrank%20discussion%E2%80%9D%20under%20the%20Human%20Rights%20dialogue.%20%E2%80%9COur%20relations%20are%20based%20on%20mutual%20respect%2C%20and%20the%20protection%20and%20promotion%20of%20Human%20Rights%20and%20fundamental%20freedoms%20are%20at%20the%20core%20of%20our%20partnership%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689250162000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13173216%2F15705313487_f92e094bb0_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Feuropean-parliament-adopts-resolution-manipur-protection-religious-minorities%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20adoption%20took%20place%20in%20the%20afternoon%20along%20with%20other%20votes%20on%20schedule%2