%20in%20Bangladesh.%20A%20retrospective%20of%20his%20work%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98Singed%20but%20not%20Burnt%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20was%20supposed%20to%20launch%20on%20July%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlam%20announced%20his%20decision%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshahidul.alam001%2Fposts%2Fpfbid0jftLSKrwv6K5iq2shUz77nY3TjeR5iGKjT7f4ienWVnG8jWsC95riMoyFPRS3NQFl%5C%22%3EFacebook%20post%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20show%20%E2%80%98Singed%20but%20not%20Burnt%E2%80%99%20which%20is%20currently%20showing%20at%20the%20Wrightwood659%20Gallery%20in%20Chicago%2C%20was%20scheduled%20to%20show%20at%20the%20Kiran%20Nadar%20Museum%20(KNMA)%20in%20Noida%20later%20this%20month.%20I%20have%20decided%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20show%20at%20KNMA.%20Last%20few%20days%20of%20show%20in%20Chicago%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fbangladesh-artist-alam-withdraws-from-knma-event-8832030%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Alam%20has%20written%20to%20Kiran%20Nadar%20explaining%20why%20he%20does%20not%20want%20to%20show%20his%20work%20at%20a%20museum%20she%20runs.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20an%20artist%2C%20journalist%20and%20human%20rights%20worker%2C%20I%20wish%20to%20express%20solidarity%20with%20the%20artists%20who%20note%20that%20in%20India%20%E2%80%98government-run%20cultural%20institutions%20have%20become%20instruments%20of%20state-sponsored%20propaganda%20rather%20than%20spaces%20for%20critical%20thinking%E2%80%99.%20The%20situation%20is%20no%20different%20in%20my%20own%20country%20Bangladesh%E2%80%A6%20There%20are%20two%20areas%20of%20concern.%20The%20clear%20endorsement%20by%20Ms%20Nadar%20of%20art%20events%20which%20are%20part%20of%20the%20propaganda%20machinery%20of%20the%20current%20Indian%20regime%2C%20and%20the%20censure%20of%20people%20who%20make%20legitimate%20critiques%20of%20such%20associations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlam%20was%20referring%20to%20Nadar%E2%80%99s%20role%20as%20advisor%20for%20the%20exhibition%20%E2%80%98Jana%20Shakti%3A%20A%20Collective%20Power%E2%80%99%20at%20the%20National%20Gallery%20of%20Modern%20Art%20in%20Delhi.%20The%20exhibition%20was%20created%20to%20mark%20100%20episodes%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20radio%20show%20%E2%80%98Mann%20ki%20Baat%E2%80%99.%20The%20other%20instance%20he%20was%20talking%20about%20was%20Sandip%20K.%20Luis%20being%20removed%20from%20the%20post%20of%20Manager%2C%20Curatorial%20Research%20and%20Publications%20at%20KNMA%2C%20following%20his%20statement%20on%20social%20media%20critical%20of%20the%20Jan%20Shakti%20exhibition%20and%20Nadar%E2%80%99s%20association%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689247840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F07163346%2Fcollage123.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fbangladeshi-photographer-shahidul-alam-pulls-out-of-knma-exhibition-criticises-kiran-nadar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alam%20was%20referring%20to%20Nadar's%20role%20as%20advisor%20for%20the%20exhibition%20'Jana%20Shakti%3A%20A%20Collective%20Power'%20at%20the%20National%20Gallery%20of%20Modern%20Art%20in%20Delhi.%20The%20exhibition%20was%20created%20to%20mark%20100%20episodes%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20radio%20show%20'Mann%20ki%20Baat'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fbangladeshi-photographer-shahidul-alam-pulls-out-of-knma-exhibition-criticises-kiran-nadar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine%20says%20downed%2020%20Russian%20drones%2C%202%20cruise%20missiles%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689246666000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101728870%2Cimgsize-91052.cms%22%2C%22originID%2