n%20a%20deal%20by%20midnight%20in%20Los%20Angeles%C2%A0(0700%20Thursday%C2%A0GMT%2FUTC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESAG-AFTRA%20said%20its%20national%20board%20would%20meet%20Thursday%20to%20vote%20on%20a%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20more%20than%20four%20weeks%20of%20bargaining%2C%20the%20Alliance%20of%20Motion%20Picture%20and%20Television%20Producers%20(AMPTP)%20%E2%80%A6%20remains%20unwilling%20to%20offer%20a%20fair%20deal%20on%20the%20key%20issues%20that%20are%20essential%20to%20SAG-AFTRA%20members%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Screen%20Actors%20Guild%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA-list%20stars%2C%20including%20Jennifer%20Lawrence%20and%20Meryl%20Streep%2C%20have%20voiced%20their%20support%20for%20the%20industrial%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20strike%20goes%20ahead%2C%20stars%20will%C2%A0not%20be%20able%20to%20promote%20new%20releases%20or%20attend%20industry%20events%20such%20as%20Comic-Con%2C%20which%20is%20set%20to%20be%20held%20next%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20union%20represents%20roughly%20160%2C000%20actors%20and%20television%20and%20radio%20presenters%20as%20well%20as%C2%A0other%20media%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20SAG-AFTRA%E2%80%99s%20demands%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20union%20is%20demanding%20higher%20compensation%20from%20streaming%20services%20as%20well%20as%C2%A0higher%20pay%20to%20counteract%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20salaries%20when%20working%2C%20actors%20earn%20%E2%80%9Cresiduals%E2%80%9D%20every%20time%20a%20production%20they%20star%20in%20is%20aired%20on%20a%20network%20or%20cable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20streaming%20services%20such%20as%20Netflix%20and%20Disney%2B%20do%20not%20disclose%20viewing%20figures%20and%20pay%20actors%20the%20same%20flat%20rate%20regardless%20of%20viewership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESAG-AFTRA%C2%A0is%20also%20demanding%20the%20implementation%20of%20safeguards%20around%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fartificial-intelligence%2Ft-42133476%5C%22%3Euse%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Actors%20want%20assurances%20that%20their%20digital%20images%20will%20not%20be%20used%20without%20their%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20SAG-AFTRA%20TV%2FTheatrical%2FStreaming%20Negotiating%20Committee%20has%20agreed%20to%20the%20AMPTP%E2%80%99s%20last-minute%20request%20for%20federal%20mediation%20and%20has%20reaffirmed%20the%20negotiating%20committee%E2%80%99s%20dedication%20to%20securing%20a%20fair%20deal%20(1%2F7)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F9gXZV6ZcRX%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F9gXZV6ZcRX%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20SAG-AFTRA%20(%40sagaftra)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsagaftra%2Fstatus%2F1679166776897306624%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2012%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20has%20happened%20in%20negotiations%20thus%20far%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20union%20negotiators%20agreed%20to%20a%20studio%20request%20to%20bring%20in%20a%20federal%20mediator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESAG-AFTRA%20said%20that%20studio%20representatives%20had%20%E2%80%9Cabused%20our%20trust%E2%80%9D%20by%20leaking%20information%20to%20the%20media%2C%20adding%20that%20there%20would%20be%20no%20change%20in%20the%20Wednesday%20night%20deadline%20that%20would%20trigger%20a%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20confident%20that%20the%20employers%20have%20any%20intention%20of%20bargaining%20toward%20an%20agreement%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20union%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20late%20Tuesday.%20%E2%80%9CTime%20is%20running%20out.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Double%20strike%E2%80%99%20could%20bring%20almost%20all%20productions%20to%20a%20halt%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C