icies%2C%20including%20land%20redistribution%20and%20securing%20tenancy%20rights%20for%20share-croppers.%20However%2C%20as%20land%20reforms%20began%20to%20be%20implemented%2C%20%E2%80%98capturing%20territory%E2%80%99%20and%20power%20in%20villages%20through%20the%20panchayat%20system%20became%20a%20part%20of%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Left%20Front%20government%20implemented%20direct%20elections%20for%20the%20three-tier%20panchayats%20under%20party%20symbols%2C%20thereby%20decentralising%20power%20and%20diminishing%20the%20influence%20of%20wealthy%20and%20influential%20families.%20This%20led%20to%20a%20transformation%20in%20the%20social%20fabric%20of%20rural%20Bengal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13152647%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-08-at-11.13.59-AM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13152647%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-08-at-11.13.59-AM.jpeg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13152647%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-08-at-11.13.59-AM-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13152647%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-08-at-11.13.59-AM-1024x576.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663006%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22607%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPeople%20queue%20to%20vote%20in%20Junglemahal%2C%20Bengal.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20study%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com.sl%2Fbooks%3Fid%3D2v-Dp9nHc3oC%26printsec%3Dfrontcover%23v%3Donepage%26q%26f%3Dfalse%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBuddhadeb%20Ghosh%20and%20Girish%20Kumar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20conducted%20in%201996%20on%20the%201993%20panchayat%20election%20found%20that%20while%20the%20panchayats%20were%20free%20from%20traditional%20elite%20domination%2C%20and%20power%20did%20become%20de-centralised%20to%20an%20extent%2C%20decision%20making%20was%20largely%20controlled%20by%20the%20party%20high%20command.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20redistributing%20land%20and%20ensuring%20the%20rights%20of%20sharecroppers%2C%20the%20Left%20government%20fought%20opposition%20from%20local%20wealthy%20families%2C%20gaining%20territorial%20control%20over%20vast%20rural%20areas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20panchayat%20elections%20too%2C%20the%20same%20locally%20influential%20families%20faced%20opposition%20from%20poorer%20candidates%20and%20these%20polls%20became%20a%20tool%20of%20class%20struggle.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBengal%E2%80%99s%20participation%20in%20rural%20elections%20was%20always%20high%20and%20thus%2C%20a%20new%20power%20structure%20emerged%20in%20rural%20Bengal%20which%20political%20scientist%20Dwaipayan%20Bhattacharya%20termed%20%E2%80%9Cparty%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20the%201990s%2C%20class%20dynamics%20gradually%20diminished%20and%20what%20remained%20was%20a%20struggle%20solely%20focused%20on%20retaining%20political%20power.%20Consequently%2C%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ecapturing%E2%80%99%20and%20control%20of%20panchayats%20grew%20into%20a%20strategic%20tool%20employed%20primarily%20to%20maintain%20political%20dominance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20decrease%20in%20agricultural%20income%20and%20a%20crippling%20lack%20of%20rural%20job%20opportunities%20in%20Bengal%2C%20panchayat%20polls%20have%20once%20again%20assumed%20a%20crucial%20role.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Those%20in%20power%20at%20the%20panchayat%20level%20can%20dictate%20job%20creation%2C%20income%20generation%2C%20and%20the%20mode%20of%20execution%20of%20government%20initiatives.%20Under%20the%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20government%20of%20the%201990s%2C%20a%20direct%20flow%20of%20funds%20from%20central%20projects%20to%20rural%20bodies%2C%20bypassing%20the%20state%20government%2C%20was%20enabled.%20This%20approach%20gained%20further%20momentum%20during%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government%2C%20and%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20has%20continued%20to%20follow%20this%20course.%20As%20a%20consequence%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20substantial%20increase%20in%20funds%20allocated%20to%20the%20panchayats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fpolicy%2Freport-summaries%2Freport-15th-finance-commission-2021-26%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E15th%20Finance%20Commission%2C%20West%20Bengal%20is%20projected%20to%20receive%20a%20sum%20of%20Rs%2017%2C199%20crore%20for%20rural%20development%20between%202021%20and%202026%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20amount%20will%20mean%20an%20average%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20per%20year%20for%20each%20of%20the%203%2C317%20panchayats%20in%20the%20state.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20direct%20fund%20transfer%20schemes%20%E2%80%93%20which%20involve%20no%20intermediaries%20and%20direct%20crediting%20to%20a%20beneficiary%E2%80%99s%20account%2C%20as%20in%20the%20MGNREGA%2C%20PM%20Awas%20Yojana%2C%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%20and%20for%20rural%20electricity%20%E2%80%93%20the%20involvement%20of%20the%20panchayat%20structure%20is%20paramount.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20This%20makes%20the%20panchayat%20it%20not%20just%20a%20political%20power%20centre%20but%20also%20one%20which%20holds%20considerable%20sway%20over%20the%20rural%20economy%2C%20directly%20affecting%20the%20lives%20of%20approximately%2070%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population.%20Controlling%20a%20panchayat%20allows%20a%20political%20party%20to%20influence%20land%20use%2C%20property%20rights%2C%20and%20resource%20allocation%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20creation%20of%20a%20beneficiary%20class%20who%20are%20expected%20to%20show%20loyalty.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConflicts%20and%20violence%20among%20political%20parties%20during%20the%20poll%20process%20is%20an%20outcome%20of%20the%20competition%20to%20gain%20control%20over%20these%20valuable%20assets%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eand%20also%20the%20rural%20society.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689242277000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13152324%2FScreenshot-2023-07-13-at-3.22.09.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbengal-panchayat-election-violence-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20state%20where%20access%20to%20political%20power%20plays%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20the%20lives%20and%20livelihoods%20of%20the%20poor%2C%20the%20competition%20to%20secure%20it%20has%20grown%20particularly%20intense.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbengal-panchayat-election-violence-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sachin%20Bansal's%20fintech%20firm%20Navi%20lays%20off%20nearly%20200%20employees%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689242039000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2014-05%2F22%2Ffull%2F1400782572-3963.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Fsachin-bansal-s-fintech-firm-navi-lays-off-nearly-200-employees-report-123071300534_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20addition%20to%20the%20layoffs%2C%20several%20individuals%20within%20the%20company%20have%20resigned%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20including%20mid-to-senior%20level%20employe