m%3ETOI%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20finance%20ministry%20must%20understand%20that%20civil%20projects%20and%20research%20projects%20have%20different%20dynamics%20and%20requirements%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fresearchers-concern-political-leadership-nrf-funds%5C%22%3EResearchers%20Express%20Concern%20Over%20Political%20Leadership%20of%20the%20NRF%2C%20Lack%20of%20Funds%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20IIT%20researcher%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20he%20last%20got%20funding%20in%202020.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20is%20getting%20funds%20from%20the%20DBT.%20On%20asking%20about%20the%20reasons%2C%20we%20are%20told%20nothing%20is%20in%20DBT%E2%80%99s%20control%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Lakhotia%20and%20others%20at%20the%20BHU%20have%20submitted%20utilisation%20certificates%20till%20March%202023.%20Yet%2C%20funds%20to%20continue%20work%20have%20not%20been%20credited%20to%20their%20accounts%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CProjects%20are%20mapped%20to%20agencies%20and%20there%20will%20be%20no%20new%20release%20order%20till%20the%20previous%20money%20has%20been%20utilised%20or%20accounted%20for%20by%20everyone%20under%20that%20agency.%20If%20any%20user%20defaults%2C%20everyone%20is%20going%20to%20suffer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20a%20lot%20of%20delays%20caused%20while%20trying%20to%20understand%20the%20new%20system%20and%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20bank%2C%20the%20money%20started%20getting%20reflected%20in%20early%20March.%20But%20on%20April%201%2C%20the%20balance%20became%20zero.%20To%20date%2C%20neither%20has%20all%20of%20the%20unspent%20balance%20come%20back%2C%20nor%20has%20any%20of%20the%20fresh%20grants%20for%20the%20new%20year%20come%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20senior%20dean%20of%20a%20STEM%20college%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3ETOI%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689237949000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13134317%2FIIT_Delhi_Entrance.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftop-researchers-face-funding-delays-lack-of-clarity-on-new-payment-system%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20funding%20delays%20have%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20made%20tall%20promises%20of%20increased%20funding%20by%20setting%20up%20a%20National%20Research%20Foundation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftop-researchers-face-funding-delays-lack-of-clarity-on-new-payment-system%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20to%20buy%2026%20Rafale%20fighters%2C%203%20Scorpene%20subs%3B%20defence%20min%20approves%20plan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689236708000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-07%2F13%2Ffull%2F1689239449-8677.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fdefence-ministry-approves-proposals-to-buy-26-rafales-from-france-123071300431_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20proposals%20were%20approved%20by%20the%20Defence%20Acquisition%20Council%20(DAC)%20meeting%20attended%20by%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajanth%20Singh%2C%20Chief%20of%20Defence%20Staff%20Gen%20Anil%20Chauhan%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fdefence-ministry-approves-proposals-to-buy-26-rafales-from-france-123071300431_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fdefence-ministry-approves-proposals-to-buy-26-rafales-from-france-123071300431_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-