ia-taste-the-history-find-your-favourite-among-28-versions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKolkata%20biryani%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Manzilat%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20I%20prepare%20%3Cem%3Ekorma%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20I%20add%20as%20a%20layer%20in%20the%20utensil.%20After%20this%2C%20I%20add%20a%20layer%20of%20boiled%20potatoes%20savoured%20with%20ghee%2C%20salt%2C%20and%20spices.%20Lastly%2C%20I%20add%20a%20layer%20of%20boiled%20rice%20and%20add%20the%20flavouring%20of%20ghee%20and%20saffron.%20When%20you%20cook%20in%20logs%20and%20%3Cem%3Ematka%3C%2Fem%3Es%20(clay%20utensils)%2C%20it%20gives%20a%20smoky%20flavour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20cook%20biryani%20with%20regular%20spices%20like%20%3Cem%3Ekebab%20chini%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20nutmeg%2C%20%3Cem%3Eshah%20jeera%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20mace%2C%20cardamom%2C%20and%20clove.%20In%20some%20Awadhi%20delicacies%2C%20I%20use%20specialised%20Awadhi%20spices%20and%20herbs%20like%20%3Cem%3Epaan%20ki%20jad%2C%20khas%20ki%20jad%2C%20patthar%20ke%20phool%20%3C%2Fem%3E(herbs).%20They%20are%20more%20aromatic.%20The%20only%20secret%20I%20have%20is%20the%20proportion%20of%20spices%20to%20be%20used%2C%20it%20makes%20a%20lot%20of%20difference%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20the%20biryanis%2C%20Manzilat%E2%80%99s%20menu%20offers%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20delicacies%20including%20Lakhnawai%20Mutton%20Yakhni%20Pulao%2C%20Chicken%20Nawabi%20Chaanp%2C%20Ulta%20Tawa%20Paratha%2C%20Fish%20Chatpata%20Handi%20Kabab%2C%20Chicken%20Lazeez%20Shami%20Kabab%2C%20and%20Shahi%20Badam%20Firni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCmf-K96hQC_%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCmf-K96hQC_%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target