2C%20and%20slowly%20started%20making%20more%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20think%20that%20cleaners%20and%20detergents%2C%20which%20dissolve%20in%20water%2C%20are%20harmless.%20When%20I%20found%20out%20that%20they%20could%20also%20be%20non-biodegradable%2C%20I%20started%20investigating%20further%20and%20switched%20to%20biodegradable%20detergents.%20When%20Abir%20started%20crawling%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20him%20to%20be%20on%20a%20floor%20that%20was%20mopped%20using%20a%20toxic%20floor%20cleaner.%20So%20I%20started%20buying%20bioenzymes%20and%20later%20made%20them%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20sustainability%20enthusiast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESonika%20then%20started%20eliminating%20plastic%20from%20her%20kitchen%20and%20reducing%20waste.%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FIMG_8484-min-1689079826-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abir%20with%20his%20bioenzymes%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FIMG_8484-min-1689079826-scaled.jpg%201920w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FIMG_8484-min-1689079826-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FIMG_8484-min-1689079826-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FIMG_8484-min-1689079826-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FIMG_8484-min-1689079826-1152x1536.jpg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FIMG_8484-min-1689079826-1536x2048.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FIMG_8484-min-1689079826-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%