n%20eye-opener.%20In%20India%2C%20most%20give%20their%20clothes%20outside%20for%20ironing.%20So%20we%20wondered%2C%20%E2%80%98Then%20why%20not%20for%20washing%3F%E2%80%99%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20we%20realised%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20more%20of%20a%20supply%20problem%20than%20demand%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Gunjan%2C%20co-founder%20and%20head%20of%20product%20and%20marketing%2C%20UClean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20attempts%20to%20uberise%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321740%2Fmother-daughters-dea-ojasvi-hema-sharma-chilzo-mumbai-global-cuisines-sauces-condiments%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaundry%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20early%202010s%2C%20but%20logistics%20remained%20a%20major%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20these%20laundry%20businesses%20operated%20through%20a%20hub%20and%20spoke%20model.%20They%20had%20their%20factories%20far%20away%20and%20logistics%20ate%20up%20their%20margins.%20Customers%20also%20complained%20about%20delays%20in%20the%20delivery%20of%20laundry.%20There%20was%20also%20an%20issue%20of%20transparency%20and%20trust.%20But%20even%20with%20these%20issues%2C%20people%20were%20giving%20their%20clothes%2C%20which%20showed%20us%20that%20the%20demand%20was%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Gunjan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20they%20decided%20to%20go%20the%20franchise%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20launched%20a%20live%20laundry%20model%20where%20everything%20is%20handled%20hyperlocal.%20Anybody%20can%20visit%20our%20laundromats%20and%20see%20our%20machines%2C%20irons%20and%20detergents%20that%20are%20being%20used.%20You%20can%20see%20how%20your%20clothes%20are%20washed.%20The%20customer%20deserves%20to%20know%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arunabh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20every%20neighbourhood%20is%20different%20in%20India%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20work%20with%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-ins