%20surrounded%20with%20fruit%20trees%20such%20as%20mango%20and%20jamun%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image--1688732294.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image--1688732294-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image--1688732294-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image--1688732294-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image--1688732294-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323062%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20idea%20behind%20the%20school%20was%20to%20give%20the%20opportunity%20students%20to%20explore%20nature.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Akanksha%20Gupta%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20a%20school%20like%20this%20is%20important%20because%20children%20do%20not%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20go%20out%20in%20the%20wild.%20As%20children%2C%20we%20had%20the%20freedom%20and%20opportunity%20to%20just%20be%20in%20nature%2C%20but%20kids%20nowadays%20spend%20most%20of%20their%20time%20on%20gadgets%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20only%20place%20they%20spent%20time%20without%20them%20is%20in%20school.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20school%20is%20the%20best%20place%20for%20kids%20to%20spend%20their%20time%20in%20nature%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaurabh%20and%20Akanksha%20have%20pursued%20their%20mission%20of%20sustainable%20architecture%20for%20years.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20our%20projects%20are%20green%20certified.%20One%20of%20our%20earliest%20school%20campuses%20was%20the%20BRCM%20school%20in%20a%20semi-arid%20zone%20of%20Haryana%2C%20constructed%20in%20the%201980s%20and%20bui