0such%20as%20accessibility%20to%20services%2C%20affordability%20of%20drugs%2C%20attitude%20and%20perceptions%20of%20care%20providers%2C%20lack%20of%20specialists%20and%20diabetes%20educators%2C%20standardised%20laboratories%20and%20treatment%20guidelines.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20is%20this%20gap%20in%20quality%20of%20care%2C%20along%20with%20mental%20health%20support%2C%20that%20Divaa%20seeks%20to%20provide%20for%20underprivileged%20children%20through%20her%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201036px)%20100vw%2C%201036px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDivaa3-1688532225.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221036%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Divaa%20conducting%20an%20awareness%20session%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDivaa3-1688532225.jpg%201036w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDivaa3-1688532225-300x209.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDivaa3-1688532225-500x348.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDivaa3-1688532225-768x534.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDivaa3-1688532225-150x104.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-322772%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22721%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDivaa%20conducts%20an%20awareness%20session%20about%20Type%201%20diabetes%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20three-pronged%20action%20plan%3A%20awareness%2C%20advocacy%20and%20funding.%20We%20are%20conducting%20awareness%20programs%20to%20educate%20adolescents%20about%20how%20to%20manage%20diabetes%20effectively.%20We%20have%20reached%20out%20to%20over%20100%20families%20of%20diabetic%20children%20in%20Karnataka.%20Endocrinologists%2C%