%20see%20which%20area%20they%20would%20like%20to%20work%20in.%20With%20Divaa%2C%20we%20saw%20that%20she%20was%20deeply%20disturbed%20by%20diabetes%20due%20to%20her%20personal%20experience.%20So%20we%20motivated%20her%20to%20create%20a%20program%20to%20create%20awareness%20about%20diabetes%20in%20underserved%20areas%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20teach%20people%20how%20to%20manage%20life%20with%20diabetes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20activate%20and%20empower%20young%20people%20like%20Divaa%20and%20teach%20them%20how%20to%20create%20impact.%20Many%20students%20want%20to%20create%20social%20change%20but%20are%20unaware%20of%20how%20to%20do%20so.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDivaa%20says%20Project%20Surya%20is%20the%20goal%20of%20her%20life%20now.%20She%20hopes%20that%20the%20government%20bans%20GST%20on%20insulin%20so%20that%20it%20becomes%20affordable%20to%20all.%20%E2%80%9COur%20vision%20is%20a%20world%20where%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F275359%2Fbugspeak-microbiome-startup-test-kit-gut-health-diabetes-health-check-bengaluru%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejuvenile%20diabetics%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20free%20of%20suffering%20and%20accessing%20insulin%20is%20easy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmain.icmr.nic.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fupload_documents%2FICMR_Guidelines_for_Management_of_Type_1_Diabetes.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EICMR%20guidelines%20for%20management%20of%20Type%201%20diabetes%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1688538711000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F